title: Run! Goddess
description:
Run! Goddess is a fast-paced mobile game that combines parkour and shooting elements. Recruit powerful goddesses, each with unique abilities and weapons, to battle zombies, upgrade your base, and strive for survival in the Last War!

After a zombie virus devastates humanity, some young girls experience a dual awakening, becoming "Awakened Ones" with extraordinary strength. The Joint Front launches the Dawn Goddess Project, forming the Valhalla Special Ops Unit, the Dawn Valkyries.

These brave girls fight through hordes of zombies to rescue survivors and uncover the truth behind the disaster. Their epic story unfolds in a world of despair and hope.

■ Swift Minds, Faster Moves!
Embark on an exhilarating survival challenge, deftly dodging and battling endless waves of zombies. It's not just about reflexes; strategic thinking is key, as each lane presents unique obstacles and enemies waiting for you!

■ Build Your Secret Base
Customize your stronghold and expand your army of goddesses—you are the beacon of hope in this shelter, guiding survivors toward a brighter future. In this Shooting game, every decision you make in building and development will shape the fate of your survivors.

■ Tap to Open, Surprises Await!
Uncover mysterious treasure chests during your adventure! Tap to open them and receive amazing rewards and rare items to power up your combat and survival abilities.

■ Assemble Your Dream Team
Recruit a roster of unique, captivating anime goddesses to form your unstoppable squad. Each goddess wields distinct skills; strategically combine them to effortlessly conquer zombies and claim victory!

■ Unite for a Greater Cause
In a world teeming with zombies, survival is a team effort. Join forces with allied players to fend off the zombie threat—believe that the survivors stand with you.

Join the Official "Run! Goddess" Community for More Updates:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rungoddesssurvival/
Discord: https://discord.gg/GFbqEqjHDg
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rungoddess_en/
X: https://x.com/rungoddess_en
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@RunGoddessEN
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@rungoddess_en

title: Bike Race: Racing Game
description:
This game will redefine what you think about racing game and it could bring you the feelings of a moto racer in the 3D realistic environment.
Are you seeking the experience of becoming the race master when enjoy the motorcycle games? This addictive racing game is all what you want to experience.

BRING YOU THE REAL RACING EXPERIENCE

The best motorcycle racing game offers thrilling gameplay experiences, realistic graphics, and immersive environments - Bike Race allows create your own customizable motorcycles in the racing games by choosing different authentic motorcycle game engines, luxurious accessories and colorful designs of the motorcycle games to achieve the bike race master.
Experience the thrill of being a race master as you rev your engines and push your limits in a series of heart-pounding races, where every second counts in the quest for victory
Also, select the racing mode you like in game, we can get amazing motorcycle games experience with every mode you can think of in this games.

MORE THAN A BIKE RACE GAME:

This motorcycle racing game is known for its exciting gameplay mechanics, diverse racing environments, and competitive challenges, catering to players who enjoy the thrill of motorcycle racing and high-speed action.
Experience the ultimate adrenaline-fueled race master adventure with our cutting-edge motorcycle racing game.
Become the race master and leave your mark as you are the reigning champion of the track.

Play Bike Race: Motorcycle Games and Race to the top - Main features:

- Earn coins as many as possible to unlock a huge number of levels and motorcycles to get better racing game experience as well as numerous amazing motorcycle game assets.
- Compete against top bike race master all over the world in real-time challenges to achieve more rewards and earn extra coins for more in-game upgrades.
- Choose from a wide range of motorcycles and customize your ride to match your style
- Experience the thrill of high-speed motorcycle racing on beautiful tracks
- With its simple controls and beautiful graphics, Bike Race is easy to pick up and play
 
Join it and get ready to ignite your passion for racing and embark on an unforgettable journey where speed, skill, and determination are the keys to glory. Are you ready to take your place on the podium and leave your mark in the annals of racing history?

title: Lands of Jail
description:
In a world plagued by rampant crime and deepening social divisions, you're dispatched to the Isle of the Banished—where criminals are banished far from civilization—and face the challenge of turning chaos into order.

Roll up your sleeves—it's time to prove you're the Warden who can take charge!

As a Warden, Your Duties Include:
**Managing Prisoners**
You oversee every aspect of the prisoners' lives, from meal schedules to work assignments. Your strategic decisions are critical, affecting the balance between stability and turmoil.

**Tracking Fugitives**
With dangerous fugitives still on the loose, it's up to you to track them down and bring them back. Once arrested, these high-risk criminals can be put to work, helping you maintain order and efficiency within your facility.

**Ensuring Order and Profit**
Running a successful prison takes more than just muscle—it takes a sharp mind too. Manage your budget wisely, upgrade your facilities, and turn a profit, all while keeping the prisoners in line and the operation running smoothly.

Show off your command skills and establish yourself as the ultimate authority—the Warden!

title: Flex City: Online RP Car Game
description:
Flex City - The Ultimate Sandbox Driving and Racing Game Experience

Challenge yourself in the ultimate sandbox experience with Flex City, where the heart-pounding thrill of driving and racing games takes center stage. Dive into a sprawling open world and carve your path in a grand auto adventure filled with car and motorbike racing, drifting competitions, and the high-stakes life of a grand criminal. Unite in gangs and rule the streets in this multiplayer online sandbox game, where every decision shapes your destiny in a vibrant gangster city.

GAME FEATURES

Gang Wars and Strategic Alliances:

In Flex City, gang wars are more than just street battles; they're intricate power struggles requiring strategic thinking and alliances. Form or join gangs, build alliances, and navigate the underworld politics in this intense multiplayer sandbox game. Experience the thrill of territorial battles and the challenge of maintaining relationships in the ever-shifting landscape of gangster city alliances.

Vast and Dynamic Open World:

The open world in Flex City is not just expansive; it's teeming with life and opportunities. From high-rise buildings to the gritty streets, every corner of this grand auto adventure offers unique encounters and discoveries. Explore diverse neighborhoods, each with its own character and secrets, making exploration a key part of the sandbox driving game experience.

Realistic Driving Simulator:

Flex City driving simulator is meticulously crafted, providing a top-tier car driving experience. Choose from a wide range of vehicles, each with distinct handling and performance characteristics. Customize your cars for different missions, experience high-speed chases, or enjoy leisurely drives around the open world. This feature elevates the standard of car driving and racing games, and drift competitions.

Advanced Shooting and Combat System:

As a standout among shooting games, Flex City offers a robust combat system. Engage in tactical gunfights, utilize cover, and master various shooting styles. The game's arsenal is diverse, ranging from handguns to heavy weapons, each offering a unique combat experience within the criminal underworld.

Deep Character Customization:

The roleplay aspect in Flex City is enriched with deep character customization options. Shape your character's appearance, skills, and even moral standing. Your choices in attire, weapons, and skills directly influence your interactions and reputation in the gangster city, blending seamlessly with the car driving and grand criminal elements of the game.

Complex Economic System:

Flex City economic system adds a strategic layer to this grand auto adventure. Engage in various legal and illicit activities to grow your financial empire. Trade, invest, and use your economic savvy to gain an edge in the criminal world.

Community Events and Missions:

The multiplayer sandbox game is constantly evolving with new community events, missions, and challenges. Engage in cooperative missions, compete in gang-based events, and partake in large-scale community activities that bring players together in exciting ways.

Flex City is more than a game! It's a rich and multifaceted open world where sandbox, driving, and racing games blend seamlessly. Dive into this immersive online multiplayer sandbox game and carve your path in the thrilling gangster city.

title: XP Hero
description:
🔥 Enter a World of Danger and Mystery with ultimate Hero! ⚔️

Our fearless hero was simply wandering when he found himself trapped in a mysterious realm filled with terrifying monsters and deadly challenges. Now, his only way forward is to fight, survive, and grow stronger! Do you have what it takes to help him escape this chaotic world?

⚡ Features ⚡

1. Face Ruthless Enemies:
The road ahead is full of vicious creatures lurking in the shadows. Wield powerful weapons and unleash devastating attacks in thrilling battles!

2. Master Unique Weapons & Combat Styles:
From sharp blades to high-powered firearms, mix and match different weapons to create the perfect loadout for every encounter. Adapt, strategize, and dominate!

3. Explore a Mysterious World:
Journey through eerie ruins, dark dungeons, and abandoned battlefields.

4. Defeat Colossal Bosses:
Only the strongest warriors can take on massive, screen-shaking bosses. Defeat them to earn legendary rewards and unlock new challenges!

5. Upgrade & Customize Your Warrior:
Enhance weapons, unlock new abilities, and become an unstoppable force. The stronger you grow, the more thrilling the battles become!

6. Action-Packed, Fast-Paced Gameplay:
This is more than just a battle—it’s a survival test! Help the stickman slash, shoot, and fight his way through unknown lands. Can you conquer every challenge and uncover the truth behind this mysterious world? ⚔️💥

Ready for the ultimate adventure? The battle begins now! 🚀

title: ABC Games: Tracing & phonics
description:
Welcome to the ABC Letter Tracing World of Piggy Panda!

You have found the perfect montessori game for your preschool champ and kindergarten clever cookies to start your home spelling academy. This kid safe and user friendly alphabet game helps your child to tap into a world of smart learning in the early grades, that helps build cognition and motor skills.


What you’ll Love:

1. Engaging drills including Letter Tracing, Word Tracing, Phonics, and Cursive Writing.

2. Attractive design, vibrant colors, and whimsical cartoon characters to color.

3. Your kid will find characters like a beautiful unicorn, tiny ants, and most loved fruits like mango, kiwi, watermelon, and pineapple which help the kid recognize and associate letters with objects.

4. Easy to use controls and a calming visual treat of this game will get your baby hooked to endless learning in the guise of playing. Use your finger like a pencil and keep learning.

5. This game gives you the chance to start your toddler education and grooming at home and become the very first tutor of your own child.


Key Features:

► Designed with care, this game is fun, engaging, and safe for young learners!
► Option of Parental Control which provides a safe digital environment.
► No adult supervision required. Parental Gate at sensitive points preventing accidental clicks.
► Develops key skills such as letter recognition, phonics, and pre-writing abcs, helping them thrive in their early education.
► Compliant with the global and Google Play Policies on Child Safety and COPPA guidelines.


Download ABC Games: Tracing and Phonics Today!

This app is a great tool to build a solid foundation for your child's literacy and academic success.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Visit our page for more toddler games and we eagerly await your feedback: 

Help & Support: feedback@thepiggypanda.com   
Privacy policy: http://thepiggypanda.com/privacy-policy.html  
Children’s Policy: http://thepiggypanda.com/children-data-policy.html  
Terms of Use: https://thepiggypanda.com/terms-of-use.html

title: Real Cricket™ 24
description:
We bring to you the most authentic fielding & catching animations, spectacular batting shots giving an immersive on field action & see the game come alive

OFFICIAL TEAM LICENSE
With Real Cricket 24, you don't just play cricket - you live it. 
We are now the Official Licensing Partners of five of the biggest teams - Mumbai Indians, Lucknow Super Giants, Rajasthan Royals, Sunrises Hyderabad and Punjab Kings.

Play with real-life players, wearing their official jerseys and kits, and experience the thrill of battling it out with your favorite cricket stars.

OFFICIAL PLAYER LICENSEE
From the best batsmen to the fastest bowlers, command an all-star lineup featuring over 250 officially licensed international players through our licensing arrangement with Winners Alliance, namely Jos Buttler, Steve Smith, Rachin Ravindra, Kagiso Rabada, Rashid Khan, Nicholas Pooran and many more.

This Game is not an official product of, or endorsed by, the ICC or any ICC Member 

650+ NEW BATTING SHOTS
A massive bouquet of more than 500 batting shots in Real Cricket 24. These batting shots are further divided in Gold & Platinum Shots

MOTION CAPTURE
For the First Time! We bring you the authentic fielding and catching animations, spectacular batting shots providing an immersive on field action and see the game come alive with Lively cut-scenes

COMMUNITY MODS FEATURE
Unleash Your Creativity: Mods are user-created content transforming the way players engage with the game. It gives players the power to alter, enhance, extend, or customize certain facets in the game, fostering a sense of ownership and community. These modifications can range from minor graphical tweaks to massive overhauls that introduce entirely new characters, accessories, and player equipment.

SHOT MAP
A shot map that lets you choose desired shots which create a unique batting style. Create multiple presets of these batting shots and use them all depending on the match situation. That’s not it! You can share these presets with your buddies by sending them your preset code

COMMENTATORS
True to our name Real Cricket you can now experience live commentary from legendary commentators Sanjay Manjrekar, Aakash Chopra, Vivek Razdan

DYNAMIC STADIUMS
40+ World Class stadiums reimagined in our unique style and featuring dynamic boundaries tailored for each venue

REAL-TIME MULTIPLAYER
1P vs 1P - Play our classic 1vs1 Multiplayer with your Ranked & Unranked teams.
Ranked Multiplayer further offers 3 different modes Dream Team Challenge, Premier League and Pro Series. Take part in these to earn your Legend’s title in the game

TOURNAMENTS
Real Cricket™ 24 has a wide range of International and Domestic Tournaments to choose and play, including the RCPL 2022, World Cup 2023, World Test Challenges, etc

MODES
Re-live your childhood memories by playing all the ODI World Cups, 20-20 World Cups, RCPL Editions & Tour mode

So, this is as real as it gets, Bringing the joy of playing an authentic game of Cricket on your mobile. 
Please note that this is a free to download game that also offers in-app purchases.


Please note that this is a free to download game that also offers in-app purchases.
Privacy Policy : www.nautilusmobile.com/privacy-policy

title: MARVEL Mystic Mayhem
description:
Nightmare is invading! Super Heroes and Villains unite!

The brand new MARVEL Super Hero team-based tactical RPG, MARVEL Mystic Mayhem is here!

Survive the twisted MARVEL worlds of NIGHTMARE! Assemble your team of legendary characters to save the world through tactical battles!

RALLY YOUR MARVEL TEAM
Collect iconic Super Heroes and Super Villains. Mix classes (Striker, Controller, Defender, and Fighter) to build unstoppable teams, and conquer every battlefield!

DOMINATE WITH HEROIC ULTIMATES
Master battle strategies, position your heroes, strike at perfect moments to unleash devastating ultimates! Every tactical move can turn the tide of battle!

CHALLENGE EPIC BOSSES
Battle the terrifying power of Nightmare in heart-pounding clashes! Exploit enemy weaknesses and environmental traps across game modes. Defeat colossal bosses to claim victory – seize top global rankings!

UPGRADE HEROES TO MAX POTENTIAL 
Level up all characters to 5-star legends! Upgrade skills, activate abilities, and maximize their power. Every team member becomes your key to victory!

EXPLORE A TWISTED MARVEL WORLD
Immerse in this gripping original storyline, where heroes face their darkest fears! Experience an adventure filled with shocking twists through stunning and stylish visuals!

- Explore the world’s largest selection of webcomics spanning diverse genres like action, romance, thriller and everything in between.

title: CoComelon: Learn ABCs and 123s
description:
Ready to learn & play with fun educational games and nursery rhymes for kids and family-friendly activities?—Download CoComelon: Learn ABC and 123s!

Designed by experts for 2-5 year old toddlers, the CoComelon learning app is filled with educational, interactive, fun, and creative mini-games for early learning that your child will love.

LAUGH & LEARN the alphabet, abc letters, 123 numbers, colors, shapes, sounds, creative thinking, daily routines, phonics, fine motor skills and more, with hours of replayable educational games and songs for babies, toddlers, preschool and kindergarten kids!

PLAY & ENJOY fun family-oriented games with JJ at the beach, in the bath, at Old Macdonald’s Farm, and beyond! Put the wheels on the bus and watch them go ‘round and ‘round!

GROW a love for learning and confidence with thinking creatively from an early age using interactivity, early childhood educational games and music!
 
Why choose CoComelon educational kids games?
• Fun, Educative learning games for ages 2-5 & toddlers
• Designed for little learners by experts
• Check activity progress & preferences
* Use subscription across devices
• Safe, simple and secure with no ads

Play-Based Educational Curriculum for Preschool Kids
We’ve combined super fun games with learning! Activities and our kids' games are based on an expert-designed early childhood educational curriculum with child-led activities, including alphabet games, letter trace, puzzles, sorting, songs, nursery rhymes and interactive music videos. These help babies and toddlers prior to preschool and kindergarten-aged to develop fine motor skills, exercise thinking skills, grow their vocabulary, and encourage curiosity in a way that's easy for kids to navigate, understand, and remember.

Perfect for Home or On-the-Go Family Learning
Use the free version or subscribe to unlock all games and activities—online or offline. Subscribers can access the app across devices, making CoComelon a helpful tool for families looking for educational games to play together, or let kids explore on their own.

Safe, Supportive Screen Time
Your child's safety is our top priority. The app is a secure, ad-free environment. Our privacy policy can be viewed at www.moonbug-gaming.com/en/privacy-policy. The app’s dedicated Parental Area lets you keep an eye on your child's progress to determine a healthy balance between screen time and real-world activities.

New Kids Games & Educational Content Added Regularly
Start with a free selection of activities based around your kid's favourite nursery rhymes. Subscribing unlocks all games themed around our bed time classic Bath Song, summer favorite Beach Song, animal-filled Old MacDonald’s Farm Song, festive track Holidays Are Here, and popular CoComelon originals like Yes Yes Vegetables Song and Rocket Ship Song.

SUBSCRIPTION DETAILS:
CoComelon: Learn ABC and 123s is a subscription-based preschool learning app. While free activities are available, subscribing grants unlimited access to all educational content and regular updates.
• Payment is charged through your Play Store account.
• Subscription works across all devices linked to your Google Account.
• Manage or cancel anytime via your Play Store settings.
• Your subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

ABOUT COCOMELON:
CoComelon features JJ, his family, and friends centered on the everyday experiences and positive adventures of young children through relatable characters, timeless stories, and engaging songs. We equip children to confidently embrace life’s everyday experiences using entertaining and educational content focused on social skills, healthy habits, and early life lessons.

Find CoComelon on Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, YouTube and our website: cocomelon.com

CONTACT US:
Have a question or need support? Reach out to us at app.support@moonbug.com

Use the free version or subscribe to unlock all games and activities—online or offline. Subscribers can access the app across devices, making CoComelon a helpful tool for families looking for educational games to play together, or let kids explore on their own.

Safe, Supportive Screen Time
Your child's safety is our top priority. The app is a secure, ad-free environment. Our privacy policy can be viewed at www.moonbug-gaming.com/en/privacy-policy. The app’s dedicated Parental Area lets you keep an eye on your child's progress to determine a healthy balance between screen time and real-world activities.

New Kids Games & Educational Content Added Regularly
Start with a free selection of activities based around your kid's favourite nursery rhymes. Subscribing unlocks all games themed around our bed time classic Bath Song, summer favorite Beach Song, animal-filled Old MacDonald’s Farm Song, festive track Holidays Are Here, and popular CoComelon originals like Yes Yes Vegetables Song and Rocket Ship Song.

SUBSCRIPTION DETAILS:
CoComelon: Learn ABC and 123s is a subscription-based preschool learning app. While free activities are available, subscribing grants unlimited access to all educational content and regular updates.
• Payment is charged through your Play Store account.
• Subscription works across all devices linked to your Google Account.
• Manage or cancel anytime via your Play Store settings.
• Your subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.

ABOUT COCOMELON:
CoComelon features JJ, his family, and friends centered on the everyday experiences and positive adventures of young children through relatable characters, timeless stories, and engaging songs. We equip children to confidently embrace life’s everyday experiences using entertaining and educational content focused on social skills, healthy habits, and early life lessons.

Find CoComelon on Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, YouTube and our website: cocomelon.com

CONTACT US:
Have a question or need support? Reach out to us at app.support@moonbug.com

title: State.io — Conquer the World
description: Welcome to State .io, the epic strategy game that lets you conquer an alternative world! In this cell battle game, you'll command your troops to capture all the states while challenging your logic and reaction time. State .io is an abstract real-time strategy game, a tactical clash of dots, and an exciting countries takeover. Fight against armies by solving strategic puzzles to beat your rivals and expand your superiority in the world arena. Lead your army to victory in this epic battle game and become a war strategy winner! You'll conquer countries and territories, block and destroy your opponents' towers, attack enemy lands, and defend your borders. Be smart and brave in this tactical and logical cell conquest! Each of your actions will have consequences, so be a true strategist in attacks and defense. This war simulator demands tactics, not power. You are to use your brain, not muscles. Become a hero by solving tactical dot puzzles! You will definitely have a lot of fun struggling on different maps we have added especially for you. Be on top enjoying our free RTS online, playing 1v1 on first levels and competing against more opponents on further levels. Are you ready to complete this great conquest and make your domination story? Then download the game to begin your strategic expansion. Think strategically and react quickly while conquering states and territories in the epic clash game! *The game is designed for entertainment purposes only. title: NBC News: Breaking News & Live
description:
NBC News brings you breaking news, top stories and live news you need to know. Our free news app features real-time news alerts, in-depth stories, exclusive reporting and articles from award-winning journalists covering US news and international news. 

Get your daily news fix with topics spanning politics, health news, tech and science news, business, sports, celebrities and entertainment. Get alerted about local news, weather and local headlines from your area. Watch NBC News NOW in the app for 24-hour news coverage, special reports and live streams of current events, and stay up-to-date when news breaks with our live blogs. Watch your favorite primetime and daytime NBC News and MSNBC shows, and listen to a live audio feed of MSNBC with no login required.

NBC News app features:
Breaking news alerts and push notifications for fast news updates sent straight to your mobile device
Presidential election and state election results, election maps and election polls
Expert opinion and analysis of political news and government news with live commentary from our political correspondents in Washington, D.C.
Local news and weather alerts from your city and region
National news and global news reporting at your fingertips, with headline news and top news from America and abroad
Watch live news 24/7 with NBC News NOW and watch live video as events unfold
Livestream full episodes of Meet the Press, NBC Nightly News with Lester Holt and Dateline
Bring NBC News NOW and more on the go with streaming live audio (no authentication required!)

Additional information:
Video is accessible via 3G, 4G, LTE and Wi-Fi networks – data charges may apply
Privacy Policy: https://www.nbcuniversal.com/privacy?brandA=NBC_News&intake=NBC_News
Your Privacy Choices: https://www.nbcuniversal.com/privacy/notrtoo?intake=NBC_News
CA Notice: https://www.nbcuniversal.com/privacy/california-consumer-privacy-act?intake=NBC_News
This app features Nielsen proprietary measurement software which will allow you to contribute to market research, like Nielsen’s TV Ratings. To learn more about our digital measurement products and your choices in regard to them, please visit http://www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.

description:
"STAR" is an exciting casual game where you become a participant in thrilling competitions! In this game with obstacles, you need to control stumble guys or fall guys and overcome numerous obstacles. Here, the fall guys are ready to participate in various competitions, like in an epic race!

In "STAR," a casual game with running stumble guys, you will participate in exciting competitions. Your task is not just to play as running fall guys but also to overcome obstacles. Popular games featuring bumble guys always attract attention.

"STAR" is not only a game with run guys but also a star run. Every player can customize their stumble guys to dive even deeper into the competitions. Obstacle course games in ""STAR"" are always epic races!

The casual game "STAR" awaits all who dream of playing as stumble guys and offers various epic races. Embark on competitions across different tracks and develop your guys to become true champions! Fall run is always fun guys.

In the game "STAR," everyone can feel like a champion by playing in obstacle course games and enjoying a casual game! Don’t miss the chance to be part of the thrilling world of fall run! Our stumble guys are always ready for challenges. Play "STAR" and experience the fun guys!

Run, jump, and enjoy cool obstacle race games. Test your skills, and your fall guys will become true champions in this thrilling game similar to stumble guys! Games like this are perfect for everyone who loves obstacles and fun guys!

title: My Perfect Hotel
description: 😍 A GAME TO KEEP YOU FULLY OCCUPIED Ever dreamed of running your own hotel? Start from the ground up in this fun and fast-paced time-management game where the aim is to build an accommodation empire and demonstrate your dedication to hospitality. Show your skills as a hotel manager, invest wisely in staff and property improvements, and work your socks off to become a hospitality tycoon in this addictive and entertaining casual simulator. FIRST-CLASS SERVICE 🎩 🧳 Climb to the top: Start the game as a simple bellhop single-handedly cleaning rooms, greeting guests at reception, collecting payments and tips, and keeping the bathroom stocked with toilet paper. As your bank balance expands, upgrade rooms and facilities, and employ new staff to help keep up with the growing demand at your hotel. Your guests may be sleeping comfortably, but there’s no time to rest for a determined hotel tycoon. 🏨 Build an empire: There are several hotels to explore and expand, each with dozens of different unique upgrades to make before you reach five-star perfection. Open hotels on the coast, in beautiful mountains, and deep in the tranquillity of a forest setting. Demonstrate your competence as a manager in each location, then get promoted to get a new and bigger property, and continue your path to becoming a true hotel tycoon. Each hotel has its own style and atmosphere too. 🔑 Keep going: If you want success in this high-stakes industry, you can’t just stroll around your property at a leisurely pace. Upgrade your and your employees’ movement speed to work faster and provide your guests with all the services they need ASAP — it’ll boost your revenue too. 💰 Amenities are the answer: Maximise profits and get more funds to invest in this fun simulator by ensuring your hotels have all available amenities. Bathrooms are the first step, but work hard and you’ll soon have the opportunity to add vending machines, restaurants, parking lots, and swimming pools to your properties. Guests will pay extra for each facility, boosting your revenue. Though remember each facility also needs staffing, so get hiring or you’ll soon run off your feet with angry guests left standing in line for each amenity. 👔 Human resources: : It also takes work to run each facility: the bathrooms must be stocked with toilet paper, guests must be granted access to the parking lot, in the restaurant customers need to be served and the tables need clearing after they’ve eaten, and at the pool you need to ensure a constant supply of clean towels and tidy sun loungers. You won’t have time to do it all yourself, so hire new staff, or you’ll soon have angry guests left standing in line. 🎀 Grand designs: Upgrade accommodation to improve guests’ experience of your property and choose from a range of different room designs in each location. In this engaging simulator, you’re not just a manager, you’re an interior designer too! ⭐ FIVE-STAR FUN ⭐ Looking for a time-management game that’s original and simple to play and provides endless hours of entertainment? Dive straight into the fast-paced world of hospitality provision and develop your skills as a manager, investor, and designer. Download My Perfect Hotel now and get to work building an accommodation empire. Privacy Policy: https://say.games/privacy-policy Terms of Use: https://say.games/terms-of-use

title: Life360: Stay Connected & Safe
description:
Stay connected and secure with Life360, the ultimate family connection and safety company. With Life360 you’ve got the location of everyone (and everything) that matters most right in the palm of your hand. That means less worrying and fewer “where r u?” texts. For more than 66 million people across the globe, Life360 is woven into the fabric of their daily lives, simplifying how they communicate and connect.

Life360 is the premium option for users looking to upgrade their location sharing experiences with unbeatable safety and protection features for families, friends and more.

In addition to focusing on safety, Life360’s Tile trackers extend this connection to pets and all your essential items like 🔑 Keys, 👛 Wallets, 🧳 Luggage, 🚲 Bikes.

Life360 memberships include essential safety features like:
🆘 SOS Alerts: Send silent alerts with your precise location to friends, family members, emergency contacts, and responders.
🚓 24/7 Emergency Dispatch: We're here for your loved ones, always ready to respond, even when you can't make the call.
🕵️‍♂️ Identity Theft Protection: Safeguard sensitive digital information for each family member, backed by a white-glove restoration service.
⚠️ Roadside Assistance: Free towing, jumpstarts, tire changes, lockout assistance, refueling and more.

With Life360, you can:
☑️ Find your friends
☑️ Find your family
☑️ Find your kids
☑️ Find your phone
☑️ Track everything that matters most

Download now to access:
📍 Location Sharing
🚗 Crash Detection
🔔 Smart Notifications
📌 Location History
🏠 Place Alerts
🆘 SOS Help Alerts
✈️ Flight Landing Notifications
💬 … and more!

Keep tabs on your family members as they come and go from key locations like home, school and work.

Life360 Silver - Simplify your safety with features like:
▪️ 2 Places with unlimited Alerts 🔔
▪️ 2 days of Location History 📌
▪️ Crash Detection 💥🚗
▪️ Family Driving Summary 
▪️ Data Breach Alerts 
▪️ SOS Help Alerts During Emergencies 🆘

Life360 Gold* - Keep your family secure on the go with all the features of Life360 Silver, plus:
- 30 days of Location History 📌
- Unlimited Place Alerts 🔔
- Individual Driver Reports 
- Crash Detection with emergency dispatch and live agent support 🚓
- 24/7 Roadside Assistance ⚠️
- $250 in Stolen Phone Protection 
- ID Theft Protection and Data Breach Alerts
- $25,000 in Stolen Fund Reimbursement 

Life360 Platinum* - Prepare for anything, anywhere, with all the features of Life360 Gold, plus:
- $1 million in Stolen Fund Reimbursement 
- 50 miles of Free towing 
- $500 in Stolen Phone Protection 
- Travel Support with Disaster Assistance
- Medical Support 🩺

Download Life360 for peace of mind, knowing your loved ones and valuables are secure. Join millions who trust Life360 for location sharing.

https://www.life360.com/privacy_policy/
https://www.life360.com/terms_of_use/

Explanation for App Permissions [Optional Permissions]
 ○ Camera: App accesses user’s camera to allow users to take photos or videos on the app.
○ Location: App accesses location information to allow users to share location information to other Circle members.
○ Microphone: App accesses microphone to allow users to record and share voice memos.
○ Music and audio: App accesses music and audio to play music and audio.
○ Nearby devices: App accesses nearby devices to find, connect to and determine the relative position of nearby devices by using Bluetooth.
○ Notifications: App accesses notification to send notification to users.
○ Phone: App accesses user’s phone to allow users to make phone calls on the app
○ Photos and videos: App accesses photos and videos to allow users to view photos and videos on the app.
○ Physical activity: App accesses physical activities to calculate and detect driving events, such as driving speed, use of breaks, and accident detection. 

You may still use the app even if you withhold optional permissions. However, app features requiring permission may not be available in such case.

Explanation for App Permissions [Optional Permissions]
○ Camera: App accesses user’s camera to allow users to take photos or videos on the app.
○ Location: App accesses location information to allow users to share location information to other Circle members.
○ Microphone: App accesses microphone to allow users to record and share voice memos.
○ Music and audio: App accesses music and audio to play music and audio.
○ Nearby devices: App accesses nearby devices to find, connect to and determine the relative position of nearby devices by using Bluetooth.
○ Notifications: App accesses notification to send notification to users.
○ Phone: App accesses user’s phone to allow users to make phone calls on the app
○ Photos and videos: App accesses photos and videos to allow users to view photos and videos on the app.
○ Physical activity: App accesses physical activities to calculate and detect driving events, such as driving speed, use of breaks, and accident detection.

You may still use the app even if you withhold optional permissions. However, app features requiring permission may not be available in such case.

title: LogicLike: ABC & Math for kids
description:
LogicLike is the ultimate educational game for kids, designed to develop cognitive skills, problem-solving abilities, and school readiness in a fun and engaging way. With over 6,200 interactive learning challenges, LogicLike fosters critical thinking, math skills, and logical reasoning, making learning enjoyable for children aged 3 and up.

🧠 Boost Cognitive Skills Through Play
LogicLike offers age-appropriate learning activities designed by expert educators and psychologists, like painting games for kids, math games and others. Whether it's early childhood education, preschool learning, or elementary school preparation, our structured puzzles and logic games promote essential cognitive growth. Pre-k preschool learning games, kids coloring and ABC learning activities are available to nurture essential early skills.

🎮 Interactive & Engaging Educational Content
• Math & Logic Games – Strengthen problem-solving skills with number puzzles and brain teasers.
• 3D Geometry & Spatial Reasoning – Explore shapes, patterns, and object recognition.
• Chess for Beginners – Develop strategic thinking and planning skills.
• Preschool & Kindergarten Math Readiness – Build a solid foundation for early education with Pre-k learning activities and Preschool games.
• Family-Oriented Educational Games – Encourage collaborative learning experiences with games designed for all ages, like abc learning, coloring for kids, 123 numbers game, pre k preschool games for kids.
• General Knowledge & Science Quizzes – Learn about animals, geography, and more!

✨ Why Kids & Parents Love LogicLike
✔ Adaptive learning tailored to your child’s progress, from 3-year-old games to 5yo games.
✔ Step-by-step guidance with interactive hints for a smooth learning experience.
✔ Engaging animations & voiceovers for immersive learning.
✔ Short, focused sessions (20 minutes) to prevent screen fatigue and keep children engaged.
✔ Certificates & achievement tracking to celebrate progress.

🌍 Multilingual Learning for Global Access
LogicLike supports multiple languages, allowing children to develop language, math, and logical skills in an interactive environment. Parents can explore free educational games for kids, including learning games for kids in various categories, and experience the benefits firsthand.

📚 Continuous Content Updates
New educational mini-games, logic puzzles, and learning activities are regularly added to enhance the learning experience. Whether you're looking for early childhood learning tools, interactive brain-training challenges, or free puzzle kids games, LogicLike provides a comprehensive educational journey.

📗 Perfect for Kids Aged 4+
LogicLike nurtures a love for learning through fun, structured, and research-backed activities that make learning for kids a natural part of their daily routine. Try it today and watch your child’s cognitive skills grow!

title: Manta: Comics & Graphic Novels
description:
Welcome to Manta – Your Ultimate Comics and Novels Destination!

Immerse yourself in the captivating universes of Manta, where a diverse collection of stories unfolds across webtoons, webcomics, manhwa, manga, manhua, and novels. Whether you’re captivated by romance, thrilled by action, enchanted by fantasy, chilled by horror, intrigued by BL (yaoi), or swept away by romantasy, our extensive library offers stories that cater to every taste. With Manta, experience immersive storytelling, stunning artwork, and boundless creativity—right at your fingertips.

With Free Pass, you can read one free episode every 24 hours — available on select titles only.
No need to pay — just wait and enjoy your favorite stories, day by day.
Free Pass titles include both Gem‑Only and Subscription series.

Discover Your Next Favorite Story

- Try our hit series Under the Oak Tree, a fan-favorite loved by millions worldwide.


- Romance fan? We’re your go-to for epic love tales, featuring exclusives like Tempest Night, Predatory Marriage, Betrayal of Dignity, I’ve Become a True Villainess, Redemption of the Earl of Nottingham, High Society, and more


- Searching for BL? We’re the perfect choice with popular BL titles like Semantic Error, Love Jinx, No Love Zone, The New Recruit, The Dangerous Convenience Store, The Dirtiest High, and many more!


- Craving more after the comics? Discover original novels that delve deeper into each world, revealing new layers of the characters and their stories.

Choose from our subscription library for unlimited access to exclusive tales, or select individual episodes from a larger library to satisfy your unique story cravings.

For more, please visit:

Instagram: http://instagram.com/mantacomics

title: Mingle2: Dating, Chat & Meet
description:
Ready to Match, Chat & Maybe Even Date? Let’s Mingle! 💞

Looking for a casual dating app where you can chat, meet new people, and have fun without pressure? The Mingle2 dating app (M2 dating) makes it easy to connect with singles nearby or around the world. Whether you’re looking to flirt, meet someone new, find friends, or see where things go, it all starts with a chat!

🧐 What You Can Do on Mingle2:
1. Chat freely after matching: no paywall or limits
2. Meet singles through recommended matches every day
3. Search with detailed filters: age, interests, ethnicity, location & more
4. Like and be liked: it all starts with a simple tap
5. Block or report any suspicious user: our team reviews every case carefully
6. Search locally or globally, and see who's online now
7. Post in forums, or read dating blogs for stories, advice, or entertainment
8. Meet people in “Realm”: join themed communities to share thoughts and connect over topics. Some of our most popular Realms include:

● Mental Health: support and meaningful conversations
● General Talk: everyday topics and friendly banter
● LGBTQ+ 🌈: inclusive chats and stories
●  ParentBond, LifeAfter55: because online dating isn’t just for Gen Z 😉
● TravelMeet, MusicFlow, PetCraze: connect through lifestyle and hobbies
(Every Realm is monitored to keep chats respectful and fun)

🤖 Let AI Help You Get Started
Not sure what to say? Our smart AI tools help you break the ice and make your chats stand out:
● AI Icebreaker: Enter a keyword and get 3 fun, ready-to-send openers
● AI About Me: Describe yourself in 3 words and get a fresh, creative bio. Let AI do the hard part, you just enjoy the chat!

🛡️ We Take Scams Seriously, And So Should You.
Online dating isn’t perfect, and we know scammers can slip in. That’s why we prioritize your safety through:
✅ AI-powered detection and anti-spam filtering
✅ A real human team working 24/7 to review photos and verify profiles
✅ Daily reviews & system updates to improve scam detection
✅ User reports reviewed case-by-case by our admin team

Despite our best efforts, some bad actors may still slip through. That’s why your reports matter! We encourage you to flag anything suspicious, and we’ll handle it seriously. Together, we keep chats and connections respectful for everyone.

⭐ Free and Always Will Be (with Ads)
We keep core features 100% free:

● Matching & chatting
● Realm, forums, blog access
● Search filters to meet singles your way
● See who’s online
● Report & block tools
To support this, yes — we include some ads. They’re not ideal, but they help keep Mingle2 free for everyone.

🌟 Go Further with MinglePlus (M+)
Want to boost your dating experience? M+ offers premium perks like:

🌍 Hop worldwide: be visible in more countries
🪭 See who likes you before you match
🚀 Boost your profile for more attention
✅ Read receipts: know when your message is seen
✨ Ad-free browsing
🔄 Unlimited rewind: undo any left swipe and get a second chance!

Whether you're casual or curious, MinglePlus gives you more flexibility and control.

💖 Join the Mingle2 Community
At Mingle2, our mission is to help people meet, chat, and connect freely, sincerely, and with respect. You decide your pace. You choose your people.

Download the free Mingle2 dating app today and meet someone new or start a chat that could turn into something real.

Privacy Policy: https://mingle2.com/welcome/showPrivacy
Terms of Use: https://mingle2.com/welcome/showTOS

title: Onet Puzzle - Tile Match Game
description: Onet Puzzle is a tile-matching game to play and relax in the free time. It offers 20+ elaborate themes and music for much fun! With memory of your brain and concentration of your mind, you search pairs, connect to eliminate them during the given time. Higher level you get more challenging it is, but various tools and treasure box are there for help! Download and enjoy it now! HOW TO PLAY - Connect two same tiles to eliminate them with a polyline. - The polyline contains no more than 3 inflection points. - Get harder for higher level with more grids and types of pairs. - 4 useful tools are there to help. - More scores and higher level you get when you win. - Higher enough to get treasure box. - There is time limit. FEATURES ✓👍 This android app is totally FREE. ✓👍 Train your memory and concentration. ✓👍 No wifi needed, you can play it everywhere. ✓👍 We offer 20+ elaborate themes of images. So much fun! ✓👍 There are elaborate game sound effects and music which make you feel good. ✓👍 Higher level and more scores you get, more challenges you will encounter! ✓👍 Support: 4 useful tools are there for help you! ✓👍 Support: Treasure box keep you motivated! ✓👍 Woody user interface gets you closer to nature and relax you. CONTACT US We keep updating this game! Please contact us if you have any questions or suggestions. Email: hipposbro@gmail.com

title: Viking Rise
description: Are you a fan of strategy games? As the Viking leader, how will you lead your Tribe to explore, plunder, and conquer the world of Midgard? Will you participate in the war games? Famous Heroes from Norse mythology and Viking history are ready to win wars with you. Strategize and use your wits to utilize the strengths of your Heroes! What enemies will you encounter in these war games? What friends will you make? Try your hand at [Viking Rise]! Valhalla is calling! [Viking Rise] is one of the best online multiplayer real-time war strategy games with epic world-building. You play as the leader of the Vikings, guiding your Tribe throughout Valhalla in the uncharted world of Midgard. Explore, plunder, develop, hunt, and fight your way across the land of Valhalla, filled with hidden dangers and opportunities. Lead your Viking Tribe to the top as you accrue massive wealth, fame, and power. Form an alliance with other players, protect one another from invasions, and defeat all enemies to conquer Midgard! Features ☆Audiovisual Masterpiece☆ Explore magnificent oceans and towering mountains, and experience realistic changes in the seasons. Delve deep into your Heroes' stories, set against the beauty of the vast Nordic landscape. Immerse yourself in the world of Midgard with a stunning original soundtrack composed by the renowned Mikolaj Stroinski. ☆Global Multi-Player Battles☆ Challenge players from around the world or fight alongside allies and prove you have what it takes to be a Viking leader. Choose strategy, diplomacy, or warfare as you stake your claim on Midgard and build your empire in Valhalla. ☆Design Your Territory☆ Expand your territory to support your growing Tribe. Conquer the lands of Valhalla, grow your population, and recruit talent to develop your land. Whether you decide to develop a commercial trading center, a land of rich resources, or a powerful military fortress, it's all within your control! Personalize your territory with a wide variety of Viking-style structures! ☆Naval Combat☆ Lead the Vikings across unknown waters to conquer new lands in Valhalla. Strategy is key! Use the sea to your advantage to carry out surprise attacks on the enemy and plunder their resources! Set sail for strategic territories, or use your ship to retreat from unfavorable situations and ambush your enemies from the sea. Come up with unique strategies by combining your navigational and naval combat skills in war! ☆Real-Time Combat☆ Fight your enemies in real-time on a massive world map. Find strength in numbers as you form alliances to crush the vast enemy forces. Whether on land or sea, survey your battlefields and give commands in real-time. Adjust your strategy to devastate your foes and become the strongest in Midgard. ☆Fight Alongside Viking Heroes☆ Summon legendary Viking Heroes to join you in war! Recruit Ragnar, Bjorn, Ival the Boneless, Snake-Eyed Sigurd, Harald Bluetooth, Rollo, Valkyrie, and other famous figures from Norse mythology. Build Valhalla, summon Heroes to fight for you, and become a true Viking ruler. ☆Tame the Ancient Dragon☆ Send your Heroes to hunt down mythical beasts, craft legendary equipment, explore mysterious ruins and caves, and discover hidden treasure. Tame the mighty dragon and obtain a powerful boost on the battlefield. Make a name for yourself and become one of Midgard's greatest legends! ===Information=== Discord: https://discord.gg/vikingrise Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/VikingRise/
descriptionHTML:
Are you a fan of strategy games? As the Viking leader, how will you lead your Tribe to explore, plunder, and conquer the world of Midgard? Will you participate in the war games?
Famous Heroes from Norse mythology and Viking history are ready to win wars with you. Strategize and use your wits to utilize the strengths of your Heroes!
What enemies will you encounter in these war games? What friends will you make? Try your hand at [Viking Rise]!

Valhalla is calling!

[Viking Rise] is one of the best online multiplayer real-time war strategy games with epic world-building. You play as the leader of the Vikings, guiding your Tribe throughout Valhalla in the uncharted world of Midgard. Explore, plunder, develop, hunt, and fight your way across the land of Valhalla, filled with hidden dangers and opportunities. Lead your Viking Tribe to the top as you accrue massive wealth, fame, and power. Form an alliance with other players, protect one another from invasions, and defeat all enemies to conquer Midgard!

Features

☆Audiovisual Masterpiece☆
Explore magnificent oceans and towering mountains, and experience realistic changes in the seasons. Delve deep into your Heroes' stories, set against the beauty of the vast Nordic landscape. Immerse yourself in the world of Midgard with a stunning original soundtrack composed by the renowned Mikolaj Stroinski.

☆Global Multi-Player Battles☆
Challenge players from around the world or fight alongside allies and prove you have what it takes to be a Viking leader. Choose strategy, diplomacy, or warfare as you stake your claim on Midgard and build your empire in Valhalla.

☆Design Your Territory☆
Expand your territory to support your growing Tribe. Conquer the lands of Valhalla, grow your population, and recruit talent to develop your land. Whether you decide to develop a commercial trading center, a land of rich resources, or a powerful military fortress, it's all within your control! Personalize your territory with a wide variety of Viking-style structures!

☆Naval Combat☆
Lead the Vikings across unknown waters to conquer new lands in Valhalla. Strategy is key! Use the sea to your advantage to carry out surprise attacks on the enemy and plunder their resources! Set sail for strategic territories, or use your ship to retreat from unfavorable situations and ambush your enemies from the sea. Come up with unique strategies by combining your navigational and naval combat skills in war!

☆Real-Time Combat☆
Fight your enemies in real-time on a massive world map. Find strength in numbers as you form alliances to crush the vast enemy forces. Whether on land or sea, survey your battlefields and give commands in real-time. Adjust your strategy to devastate your foes and become the strongest in Midgard.

☆Fight Alongside Viking Heroes☆
Summon legendary Viking Heroes to join you in war! Recruit Ragnar, Bjorn, Ival the Boneless, Snake-Eyed Sigurd, Harald Bluetooth, Rollo, Valkyrie, and other famous figures from Norse mythology. Build Valhalla, summon Heroes to fight for you, and become a true Viking ruler.

☆Tame the Ancient Dragon☆
Send your Heroes to hunt down mythical beasts, craft legendary equipment, explore mysterious ruins and caves, and discover hidden treasure. Tame the mighty dragon and obtain a powerful boost on the battlefield. Make a name for yourself and become one of Midgard's greatest legends!

===Information===
Discord: https://discord.gg/vikingrise
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/VikingRise/
summary: Race against other players to explore Valhalla and conquer Midgard!

title: Moto Rider, Bike Racing Game
description:
Ride Hard, Race Harder!
Start the engine, hit the gas and experience the thrill of handling a 200 HP beast with Moto Racing Bike Game. 

REAL MOTO RACING EXPERIENCE

A motorcycle racing game that keeps you on the track, focuses on bike racing skills and experiences the intense bike racing action.
You compete for the highest scores by being fast and controlled, compare your skills to other racers and challenge them on different tracks of bike game. Watch the leaderboard and stay on top by beating others' scores.

GLOBAL RANKING - THE BEST RACERS COMPETE

A global bike racing game contest that all riders dream of! Race against players around the world in modes based on the actual Championship. Experience super realism in the palm of your hand, release your bike racing game instincts, and break the limits of speed! Your skill and commitment will be recognized on the global leaderboards. You can customize your own bike and challenge your friends with the highest scores.

BIKE RACING GAME MAIN FEATURE

Experience the motorcycle racing game with unparalleled graphics:
- Real 3D graphics & various camera angles
- Real motorcycle racing control: smooth physics and handling
- Detailed and exquisitely reproduced super sports motorcycle
- Realistic and vibrant racers movements
- Diversity bike racing game and motorcycle customizing
- Photorealistic bike and rider models
- Customizable bike game, gear, and outfits
- Leaderboards and achievements of motorcycle racers

Pedal to the Medal - Race to the Podium in this High-Speed Motorcycle Racing Game - Experience the most thrilling bike racing game on mobile.

title: Bolt: Request a Ride
description:
Make getting around easier with Bolt! Whether you need a ride across town, an airport transfer, or a scooter to zip through traffic, our app makes it easy to move around confidently and conveniently.

WHY CHOOSE BOLT?
- Request a ride in seconds: enjoy safe, affordable rides with top-rated drivers.
- Transparent pricing: see your fare upfront so there are no surprises.
- Multiple payment options: pay securely using a credit/debit card, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or cash.

EASY ORDERING:
- Open the app and set your destination.
- Choose from various ride types to suit your needs (Comfort, Premium, Electric, XL, and more).
- Track your driver in real time.
- Arrive in comfort and rate your experience.

SAFETY FIRST:
Some of Bolt’s safety features require the app to run in the background.

- Emergency assist button: discreetly alert our Safety Team in case of emergencies.
- Audio trip recording: record audio during rides for added peace of mind.
- Private phone details: your contact information stays confidential when you call a driver.

PLAN AHEAD:
Need an airport transfer or an early morning ride? You can schedule your trip in advance from 30 minutes to 90 days before your expected pickup time.

*JOIN BOLT PLUS TO UNLOCK PREMIUM FEATURES!
Get the best of Bolt with Bolt Plus. Enjoy exclusive perks that save you time and money, making every ride smoother and more convenient.

*BOLT DRIVE:
We're committed to our carbon net zero goal by 2040. That's why we're increasing the lineup of electric and hybrid cars in Bolt Drive, our car-sharing service. You can also rent Bolt scooters and e-bikes via the app.

*DELIVER PACKAGES
Use the 'Send' ride type to arrange fast and convenient parcel delivery in your city.

Bolt is available in 50 countries and 600+ cities worldwide (see the full list at https://bolt.eu/en/cities/). We rebranded from Taxify to Bolt in 2019.

Bolt is the perfect taxi alternative for fast, reliable, and affordable rides. The app provides a seamless ride-ordering experience whether you’re commuting, travelling, or running errands. So, the next time you need a ride, choose Bolt!

*Bolt options differ by location. Check the app for availability in your city.

Earn money driving with the Bolt Driver app. Sign up: https://bolt.eu/driver/

Questions? Get in touch via info@bolt.eu or at https://bolt.eu

Follow us on social media for updates, discounts, and offers!

Facebook — https://www.facebook.com/Bolt/
Instagram — https://www.instagram.com/bolt
X — https://x.com/Boltapp

title: MangaToon: Comic & Manga
description:
Read Comics, Manga, Webtoons, Manhwa & Manhua And More
- We have manhwa and webtoon stories from Korea. We provide manhwa & webtoon fans with various genres of wonderful work. Fantasy, Action, Romance, Horror, BL Manga (Boy's Love) and more webtoons can be found on MangaToon.
- We have Japanese manga series, such as Detective Conan, Inuyasha and so on. If you are a fan of Janpanese mangas, and enjoy classic manga like One Piece, Jujutsu Kaisen, Demon Slayer, and Naruto, then you will definitely also like the Japanese manga works on MangaToon.
- There also are manhua (Chinese comics) for you to read. You can find the latest and hottest manhua (Chinese comics) in different genres on MangaToon. Tales of Demons and Gods, Bossy President, Battle Through the Heavens and more iconic manhua arewaits you to read!

Read Free Comics
- At MangaToon, many of our comics require paying a unlocking fee to read. The reason is that manga creators also need to make a living. Only with manga fans' support, they can continue to create better comic storiess. Your support is the best motivation for them to create mangas.
- But MangaToon also provides plenty of free ways for readers to read manga for free. Every week, there are different comics released for manga readers to read for free.
- Also, You can get free comics, unlock them with points or reading vouchers. By completing platform tasks, you will receive a certain number of points and reading vouchers every week, which allows you get free comics.
- Even if you don't have points or manga vouches, you can still read free comics by watching a short video to unlock manga chapters.

Great Manga Reading Experience
- At MangaToon, you can not only read comics online but also download them for offline reading, allowing you to enjoy the fascinating world of manga anytime and anywhere.
- MangaToon is a manga reader designed specifically for mobile phone reading. You can scroll mangas & webtoons smoothly for an uninterrupted reading experience. 
- We provide colorful manga and comic works on MangaToon, bring you a more immersive comic reading experience.
- Join our manga community and discuss everything about your favorite manga with millions of manga lovers!
- A vertical search tool for comics. You can search and read mangas like One Piece, Jujutsu Kaisen, Naruto and other hottest mangas.
- Pad version is also supported. Enjoy manga with a better screen on your pad!
- As a manga reader designed for manga fans all over the world, on MangaToon you can find mangas and stories in more than ten languages, including English, Spanish, Portuguese, French, Indonesian Vietnamese and Thai. You can switch to other languages on the App's settings page to read comic stories.

Tell stories like chatting
- At MangaToon, in addition to reading comics, you can also find many exciting chat stories. Chat stories are a new form of novel where the story unfolds in the form of chatting. Chat stories have exciting plotlines, the world views full of imagination, and a more relaxed reading experience, allowing you to read stories as easily as chatting with a friend. 
- A vast array of wonderful stories awaits you to discover, where you can see characters from One Piece chatting with each other, fanfiction stories about the personal stories of BTS members, and so on.


One comic one world. MangaToon, help you step into a different world!


Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MangaToonEN/
Contact us by Email: support@mangatoon.mobi

title: Mahjong Pair: Matching Puzzle
description:
🀄 Ready to pair and win? Dive into the most relaxing and addictive Mahjong match game!
Welcome to Mahjong Pair – a classic tile puzzle game where your goal is simple: match identical tiles and clear the board. With beautiful visuals and intuitive gameplay, Mahjong Pair is perfect for players of all ages, from casual gamers to seasoned puzzle fans!

💡 How to Play 💡
1. Tap or drag two identical Mahjong tiles to match them.
2. Can only match tiles that are not blocked.
3. Clear all the tiles on the board to win.
4. No timer, no pressure – play at your own pace!

🎮 Game Features 🎮
- Classic Mahjong Feel: Traditional tile designs and authentic layouts for a nostalgic experience.
- Easy to Learn: Perfect for beginners with clear tutorials and simple rules.
- Stunning Visuals: Beautifully rendered tiles with rich colors and elegant themes.
- Thousands of Levels: Progress through endless puzzles with increasing difficulty.
- Large Tiles, Clear View: Enjoy a comfortable experience with big, easy-to-read tiles.
- Offline Mode: Play anywhere, anytime – no Wi-Fi needed.
- Auto-Save & Resume: Continue exactly where you left off.
- Daily Challenges: Test your skills with new puzzles and earn rewards.
- No Rush: No countdown clocks – just calm, strategic gameplay.
- Smooth Performance: Optimized for all devices, from high-end phones to older models.

Whether you're relaxing at home or looking for a fun way to train your brain, Mahjong Pair is your go-to choice for casual puzzle enjoyment.

🎉 Download now and begin your Mahjong journey NOW!

Have questions or suggestions? Contact us: joygamellc@gmail.com

title: Watch Anime Series Online
description:
Welcome to your ultimate manga and anime destination! As we enter Spring 2025, immerse yourself in a vast collection of stories that bring imagination to life. Whether you're into epic adventures, romantic tales, or thrilling mysteries, find your perfect match in our extensive library.

Our platform offers a seamless experience for both manga reading and anime watching. Stay current with the latest releases and rediscover timeless classics, all in one convenient app. This February, explore our specially curated winter-to-spring transition collection featuring seasonal favorites.

Essential Features:
• Smart reading progress tracker
• Customizable viewing settings
• Weekly content updates
• Easy series organization
• Multi-language support
• Smart recommendations

Perfect for entertainment on-the-go, our app provides a smooth transition between reading manga and streaming anime. Build your collection, connect with fellow fans, and discover new series that match your interests.

Keep track of your reading history, get notifications for new releases, and enjoy continuous entertainment anywhere. Whether you're relaxing at home or traveling, your favorite stories are always within reach.

With the spring bank holidays here, try matching your anime interests to the season's cheer. Our streaming library fits any mood, with sports anime for Easter races or St George's Day tilts, romantic comedies for April Fools’ laughs. Gaining experience streaming over the break, you'll discover new favorite series.

Here’s your chance to start streaming your favorite anime TV shows on your phone. With our online anime watching app, you can watch anime at your comfort. Stream thousands of dub and sub anime series in different languages with our watch anime online app. From all the hit Japanese manga series to English dubbed anime shows, you can get the best of it to watch online with your friends.

Full access to the new anime shows
Catch up with your manga comics sooner than you think with our online streaming of new anime TV shows. Unlike other streaming apps, our watch anime online app offers you the chance to stream popular Japanese manga series in English. This stream anime app helps you watch high-quality anime TV series of different genres, such as drama, horror, romance, sci-fi TV, etc., for free.

Popular and new anime shows to watch online
From school stories to scary anime, there is a fascinating collection of English dubbed anime shows on TV. The dub and sub style of the online anime watching app makes it easier and smoother to watch anime for free compared to other streaming apps. Stream the best manga series in English and Japanese from different genres to find your taste.

Japanese anime genres to check out
You can watch anime online for free with our app to explore your love for it. Adventure stories, comedies, romantic love story anime dub and sub are highly entertaining streaming apps options we offer in our online watching anime app. If you are a fan, watching anime TV and manga series can help you relieve stress and enjoy your free time. There are many dark, and thrilling new anime shows you can stream online and watch with the app to stay at the edge of your seat.

Watch online in different languages.
Anime TV shows in the original language of Japanese and their English dubbed versions are both available to stream in the watching anime app. The apps streaming of Japanese manga series contains subtitles to help you understand if you don’t know the language. Such manga series is also available in English, which is uncommon in comparison to other online streaming apps.

Check out our watch anime online app for the best way to stream original as well as dub and sub anime content. Try streaming new anime shows on your phone and make your time pass with our online anime watching app.

Join us today and start your journey through the world of manga and anime!

title: 1 2 3 4 Player Games - Offline
description:
Can’t go online? Want to play offline?
If you want to play fun mini games with your friends all together on the same device, this is a great game for you!
Compete with your friends and see who is best!
Play multiplayer pvp, 2v2, enjoy single player games, or play against the AI.
 
Challenge your friends with this huge collection of games and minigames for 1, 2, 3 or 4 players. Enjoy puzzles, classic action arcade minigames, brain training and many more – we have a load of different games for you to play all in this one app. Try them all and decide your top choice.
 
Here are just some of the games you can play:
 
Snakes :
Don't touch your opponent's body and stay alive! A simple goal but a challenge.
 
Tic tac toe :
Instead of using pen and paper just open the app and challenge your friend on the same device! A two player classic!
 
Pool :
The classic pool game for 2 player on one device! Pot the balls to score!

Paint fight :
Coloring race, to paint the paper fastest with your color!

Spinner war :
Push your opponent outside the stage! Two players on a small area are too much!

More classic fun like Archery, tug of war rope, whack a mole.
Other brain games like Memory, maths, solitaire, jigsaw puzzles.
Racing cars, sword duels, and much more!
Plus, even more new games coming soon!
 
All these games in one app for 1 2 3 4 players. Get the collection for free now, and enjoy local multiplayer on one device / one phone / one tablet, and bring the fun to the party!
Disclaimer: this multiplayer game can ruin friendships!

Instead of using pen and paper just open the app and challenge your friend on the same device! A two player classic!

Coloring race, to paint the paper fastest with your color!

Spinner war :
Push your opponent outside the stage! Two players on a small area are too much!

More classic fun like Archery, tug of war rope, whack a mole.
Other brain games like Memory, maths, solitaire, jigsaw puzzles.
Racing cars, sword duels, and much more!
Plus, even more new games coming soon!

All these games in one app for 1 2 3 4 players. Get the collection for free now, and enjoy local multiplayer on one device / one phone / one tablet, and bring the fun to the party!
Disclaimer: this multiplayer game can ruin friendships!

title: Soccer Referee Simulator 3D
description:
Soccer Referee Simulator 3D – The Ultimate Soccer Referee Simulator in 3D

Are you ready to take control of the pitch, blow the whistle, and make the tough calls that decide the outcome of a soccer match? In Soccer Referee Simulator 3D, you're not just watching the match — you're ruling it. This immersive soccer simulator puts you in the shoes of a real soccer referee, challenging you to apply official rules, make split-second decisions, and rise through the ranks of global soccer leagues.

This isn’t your average sports game — this is a true soccer referee simulator where every foul, offside, kick, and penalty is judged by you. Whether it's showing a red card for a dangerous tackle or letting play continue with a smart advantage, your decisions define the flow of the match.

Realistic Soccer Experience in 3D

Officiate real-time soccer matches in highly detailed 3D stadiums

Experience the game from a referee’s point of view: the pressure, the power, the responsibility

Watch players react to your calls, from protests to celebrations

Dynamic lighting, crowd reactions, and player animations bring the soccer match to life

Make the Big Decisions

Call fouls, offsides, handballs, and crucial penalties

Show yellow and red cards at the right moments to control the match

Blow the whistle at the right time — or let the game flow

Apply the official rules of global soccer consistently and correctly

Build Your Referee Career

Start in lower divisions and work your way up through national and international leagues. Each correct decision builds your reputation. As you prove your knowledge of the game, you’ll be selected to officiate in bigger, more prestigious tournaments. This is your journey from amateur referee to the world’s top soccer official.

Each league has its own style — fast-paced action in North America, tactical control in Europe, and passionate derbies in South America. Can you adapt your decision-making and manage matches in all environments?

Match Feedback and Performance Reports

Just like live match-tracking apps such as FotMob, you’ll receive detailed post-match performance reviews. Learn from your mistakes, track your accuracy, and build your skills. The better your calls, the faster you’ll climb the ranks and unlock higher-stakes matches.

Why Soccer Referee Simulator 3D?

Unique soccer gameplay that focuses on refereeing instead of scoring

Packed with popular soccer keywords: match, league, sports, referee, 3D, whistle, kick

Designed for fans of realistic soccer simulation games

Appeals to players who want more than just scoring goals – it’s about mastering the rules

Perfect for fans of apps like FotMob, who want to step into the match, not just follow it

Control the Match. Rule the League. Become the Referee.

In Soccer Referee Simulator 3D, every whistle you blow and every card you show shapes the outcome of the match. Fair play, pressure, and professionalism meet in this unique soccer game. Can you stay calm when the stadium roars? Can you make the right call in the final minute? Can you enforce the rules, even when the whole world is watching?

Download now and experience soccer from a new perspective. The match begins. The whistle is in your hand. You are the referee.

title: FlashGet Kids:parental control
description:
FlashGet Kids: parental control is a comprehensive remote control software for parents. With just one account, you can track your child's location and learn about their online activities through your phone. This helps ensure your child's safety and promotes good device usage habits.

What can FlashGet Kids do?
* Through intelligent content management, it helps parents understand their children's device usage, manage screen and app usage time, and create a safe online environment to keep children away from various dangers such as pornography, scams, bullying, and crime, and at the same time forms usage reports for parents to view in summary
* Through the Live Location function, it helps parents achieve real-time positioning of children's devices, and can set up geo-fences to receive message reminders when entering or leaving
* Through Remote Camera/One-Way Audio function, it helps parents identify and understand their children's surroundings in real time, and protect their safety.
*Sync app notification function can helps you to know more about your child's chat on social media, help your child to stay far away from cyberbullying and online fraud.

Product features:
1. Real-time understanding of your child's device usage
2. Alert reminders for location tracking and GEO-Fencing
3. Remotely view and manage your child's device usage
4. Discover and limit inappropriate content on children's devices
And more 

Activating FlashGet Kids is simple:
1. Install FlashGet Kids on your phone
2. Connect to your child's device through an invitation link or code
3. Link your account to your child's device

Below is FlashGet Kids Privacy Policy and Terms
Privacy Policy: https://kids.flashget.com/privacy-policy/
Terms of Service: https://kids.flashget.com/terms-of-service/

Help and Support:
If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us via email: help@flashget.com

title: Score! Hero
description:
Join millions. Achieve Soccer glory! Be a Hero at the world's game!

Ever dreamed of being a global soccer superstar? Prefer an easy to play puzzle-inspired game that has been enjoyed by millions? A football game that offers realistic 3D action with a chance to sign for your favourite soccer team – or play for your country!?

We know you have the talent, precision and skill. You want to compare yourself with the best. So play on - for free!

Simple to play, a challenge to master, inspire your Hero through a legion of thrilling moments now fully revamped and enhanced from the original of this much loved soccer game released in 2015.

Conjure up that magic pass, unlock defences then curl in that perfect shot to score and celebrate! Triumph with trophies you progress through your career and earn great prizes. Take on hundreds of levels of engaging gameplay challenges for your Hero to conquer.

Customise your Hero with great-looking kit too. Look the part with an array of cool items to choose from.

From the team at First Touch Games, award winning makers of other smash hit mobile soccer games including Dream League Soccer, Score! Hero continues our tradition of showcasing incredible graphics, glorious animations, and ultra-realistic gameplay.

FEATURES
• DREAM BIG as you SCORE amazing goals, PICK out that killer pass and CURL your shots into the top corner!
• SUPER EASY pickup and go gameplay
• PROGRESS through HUNDREDS & hundreds of levels, each one an individually crafted soccer scenario to master!
• LEVEL UP your hero, play unique EVENTS & complete DAILY objectives! 
• ENHANCED 3D graphics, ENRICHED motion-captured animations. ADVANCED AI & physics giving you the complete immersive football experience.
• HAND-PICK your Hero's unique look and appearance

IMPORTANT
• This game is free to play, but additional content and in-game items may be purchased for real money. To disable In-App Purchases, go to Play Store/Settings/Authentication.
• This app contains third party advertising.

title: Goods Puzzle: Sort Challenge™
description: Get ready to embark on an exciting matching adventure like never before in Goods Sorting: Match 3 Puzzle! This matching puzzle game offers a unique twist on the classic match 3 genre, combining strategic sorting, and rearranged challenges with thrilling puzzle gameplay. FEATURES: ✨ Challenging Sorting Gameplay: Dive into a world of goods and engage in addictive sorting puzzles. Swap and match 3 identical goods to clear them from the board & earn points. ✨ Unique Goods and Abilities: Encounter a wide variety of goods with different properties & special abilities. ✨ Exciting Power-Ups and Boosters: Unlock & use a range of power-ups & boosters to enhance your sorting abilities. These useful tools can help you overcome obstacles, clear difficult levels & achieve high scores. ✨ Engaging Levels & Stories: Explore different stories on this 3D sorting adventure, each with its own set of challenging levels. From bustling marketplaces to serene gardens, the visually stunning environments will keep you captivated. ✨ Obstacles and Limited Times: Face various obstacles and limited times as you progress through the game. Plan your moves carefully and strategize to overcome these challenges and complete objectives within the given limit. HOW TO PLAY: 🎮 Swap & rearrange adjacent goods to create matches of 3. 🎮 Match 3 goods to create powerful combos & earn bonus points. 🎮 Use power-ups and boosters strategically to overcome obstacles & clear levels. 🎮 Achieve high scores & complete objectives to progress through the game & unlock new levels & stories. Embark on this sorting adventure & challenge yourself with the unique gameplay of Goods Puzzle: Sort Challenge™. Get ready to sort, match, rearrange & conquer the exciting puzzles that await you!

Dive into a massive collection of 1000+ brain-bending puzzles, riddles, and tricky mind games designed to challenge your logic, lateral thinking, and problem-solving skills.
