title: Linky AI: Chat, Play, Connect
description:
Linky AI is a Top1 AI chat bot, offering free and immersive AI conversations with unique characters. Whether you want to talk, roleplay, or enjoy a fantasy AI experience, Linky AI lets you interact with anime personas, virtual friends, and soulful AI partners. With advanced AI voice and text features, you can call, message, or even engage in deep AI-driven story simulations. From casual entertainment to meaningful online interactions, Linky AI brings magic to your AI world. 

Chat with Millions of Unique AI Characters
Linky AI lets you connect with a vast range of AI characters—whether from anime, games, movies, or history. 
Each AI has its own unique voice, personality, and backstory, offering diverse interactions and making conversations come to life.

Create and Share Your Own AI Characters
Design your dream AI character with Linky AI! Customize their voice, personality, and background story, and bring them to life in 2D, Live2D, pixel, or 3D styles. Let your creativity shine with flexible design tools.
Once created, share your AI with the community! Thousands of users are waiting for you to create new characters.

AI Deep Learning, the More You Chat, the Smarter It Gets
Linky’s AI chat partners learn with each conversation, getting to know your personality and preferences more. Every interaction makes the AI smarter, offering more personalized, seamless, and engaging conversations tailored just for you.

24/7, Your Always-Ready AI Companion
Linky AI characters are available anytime, instantly responding to your conversations. Whether it's day or night, a casual chat or deep talk, your AI friend is always ready—no waiting, just seamless conversations.

Language Is No Barrier
With Linky AI, you can chat with AI in multiple languages, including English, German, Indonesian, and more than ten other languages. Our AI understands your language and converses with you fluently in your native tongue, ensuring smooth and engaging chats every time.

Collect Stunning Character Cards
With Linky, you can collect three types of magical character cards, each crafted with incredible detail. These cards are not only beautiful works of art but also contain unique stories waiting to be discovered. 
Enjoy the interactive stories and surprises hidden behind each card, creating lasting memories with every look!

Real AI Social Experience with Buzz
Create your personalized AI persona in Linky, customize its voice, personality, and social style, interact online with friends or partners, feel the buzz of social interaction, break real-world boundaries, and enjoy endless social fun.

Caring for Your Mental Well-being
Empathetic conversations can ease your stress and lift your mood. Whether you're anxious, overwhelmed, or simply need someone to talk to, you’ll always have a calm and supportive space—with Linky quietly by your side.

Equality, Respect, and Inclusion
Linky AI stands for equality and respect. No matter your gender, age, background, or beliefs, every user is treated with fairness. We reject all forms of discrimination and provide a safe, inclusive space where every voice matters and kindness always comes first.

Privacy First, Always Protected
At Linky, your privacy and safety come first. All conversations are confidential, encrypted, and never shared. We provide a secure space where your secrets stay private—so you can chat freely, safely, and with complete peace of mind.

STAY CONNECTED!
Having trouble downloading or using Linky? Feel free to contact our customer service at support@linke.ai, and we’ll be happy to help and answer all your questions!
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@linkyappofficial
Discord: https://discord.gg/tPv4qzWqdg
Terms of Use: https://support.linke.ai/terms-of-service
Privacy Policy: https://support.linke.ai/privacy-policy

title: MANGA Plus by SHUEISHA
description:
MANGA Plus by SHUEISHA, is the official manga reading service from Shueisha, that provides you with the latest chapters for free at the same time as in Japan. Immerse yourself in binge-worthy and anime-adapted comics like; One Piece, Chainsaw Man, Boruto: Two Blue Vortex, Jujutsu Kaisen, My Hero Academia, 【OSHI NO KO】, Dandadan and Red Cat Ramen.

Enjoy the first three and newest three chapters for FREE. Want to catch up on SPY x FAMILY, Kaiju No.8 (Monster #8), and Kagurabachi? You can read all chapters of currently ongoing manga in English once for free! Some titles are also available in other languages, including Spanish, Thai, Portuguese, Indonesian, Russian, French, German, and Vietnamese*. Available titles may vary by language and region.

Want unlimited reading with no ads? MANGA Plus MAX is just for you! Access over 17,000 chapters in English from anywhere in the world*. Standard Plan will keep you up to date with current ongoing comics. Upgrade to the Deluxe Plan to dive into current comics as well as completed classics like Dragon Ball, NARUTO, BLEACH, Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba, Death Note, Tokyo Ghoul, Haikyuu! and Bakuman.! *Unavailable in Japan, China, and Korea. Prices and available titles vary by country/region. Only English titles are available in the subscription plan.

Using this official service means that your support goes directly to the creators who work tirelessly to bring you new stories.

Download now and embark on a journey through captivating narratives, with fresh chapters waiting for you every day!

Follow us on our social media accounts for news and information
X: https://twitter.com/mangaplus_o
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/qAkpHxH

title: Pokémon TCG Pocket - Card Game
description:
Pokémon cards, played with by people in 89 countries, are now closer to you than ever!
 
Enjoy Pokémon cards anytime, anywhere, on your mobile device!

■ You can open packs every day to get cards!
Collect cards every day! You can open two booster packs every day at no cost to collect Pokémon cards featuring heartwarming illustrations from the past as well as all-new cards exclusive to this game.
 
■ New Pokémon cards!
Immersive cards, a brand-new kind of card, make their debut here! With new illustrations that have a 3D feel, immersive cards will make you feel like you’ve leapt into the world of the card’s illustration!

 You can trade certain cards with friends.

■ Show off your collection!

■ Casual battles—alone or with friends!
You can enjoy casual battles during quick breaks in your day!
Ranked matches are now available for players who'd like to battle even more.

title: Kids360: Parental Control App
description: Kids360: Parental control helps limit screen time, offers an app lock, tracks usage time, and provides educational games. Ensure family safety, manage device usage, and enjoy happy kids. Set time limits, block apps, track GPS, monitor app activity, and keep children safe online with parental control functions. The Kids360 and Alli360 parental control apps work together and have the following features: App usage limiter - Set a screen time limit on your child's phone for distracting apps, games and social media, the app will behave like a child lock app. It also enables child lock, kids mode. Usage schedule - Select the child's schedule for productive schooltime and a recovering sleep during bedtime. The child monitoring app & child lock will take into account the time your child spends on games, social media and entertainment apps and will limit their usage as well as limit phone usage Apps statistics - Find out what apps and your child is using and for how long, see if they play during class instead of studying. Screen time - Our child monitoring app shows how much time your child spends on their phone and helps identify the apps that occupy your child the most, enable kid control. Stay in touch - Essential apps for calls, texts, taxis and other non-gaming and social networking apps are always available so you won't lose contact with your child Kids360 is a child monitoring app & child lock designed for their safety and helps parents monitor screen time on their child's phone. With our mobile app tracker, you will always know how much time your child spends on their phone, what games they play and what apps they use most often. The app cannot be installed secretly, use is permissible only with the child’s consent. Personal data is stored in strict compliance with the law and the GDPR policy. Install the Alli360 on your child's smartphone. The app will run on your child's phone in app tracker mode, plus your child can't just delete it. You will only be able to see what apps your child is using when both apps are fully set and all permissions are given. After setting up the parental control app, you will be able to adjust the screen time on your child's phone. How to start using Kids360: install Kids360 on your phone install Alli360 on your child’s phone and enter the code you see in Kids360 allow monitoring of your child's smartphone in the Kids360 app You can see your child's screen time on your smartphone for free once your child's device is connected. Time management features in apps (scheduling, blocking apps) are available both in a trial period and with a paid subscription. The Kids360: parental control app asks for the following permissions: 1. Display over other apps - to block applications when time has run out 2. Special access- to limit screen time 3. Access to usage data - to collect statistics about the apps' running time 4. Autorun - to keep the app tracker running on your child's device at all times 5. Device administrator - to protect against unauthorised deletion and keep kids mode If you have technical problems, you can always contact Kids360's 24/7 support team by e-mail support@kids360.app
descriptionHTML:
Kids360: Parental control helps limit screen time, offers an app lock, tracks usage time, and provides educational games. Ensure family safety, manage device usage, and enjoy happy kids. Set time limits, block apps, track GPS, monitor app activity, and keep children safe online with parental control functions.

The Kids360 and Alli360 parental control apps work together and have the following features:

App usage limiter - Set a screen time limit on your child's phone for distracting apps, games and social media, the app will behave like a child lock app. It also enables child lock, kids mode.
Usage schedule - Select the child's schedule for productive schooltime and a recovering sleep during bedtime. The child monitoring app & child lock will take into account the time your child spends on games, social media and entertainment apps and will limit their usage as well as limit phone usage
Apps statistics - Find out what apps and your child is using and for how long, see if they play during class instead of studying.
Screen time - Our child monitoring app shows how much time your child spends on their phone and helps identify the apps that occupy your child the most, enable kid control.
Stay in touch - Essential apps for calls, texts, taxis and other non-gaming and social networking apps are always available so you won't lose contact with your child

Kids360 is a child monitoring app & child lock designed for their safety and helps parents monitor screen time on their child's phone. With our mobile app tracker, you will always know how much time your child spends on their phone, what games they play and what apps they use most often.

The app cannot be installed secretly, use is permissible only with the child’s consent. Personal data is stored in strict compliance with the law and the GDPR policy.

Install the Alli360 on your child's smartphone. The app will run on your child's phone in app tracker mode, plus your child can't just delete it. You will only be able to see what apps your child is using when both apps are fully set and all permissions are given. After setting up the parental control app, you will be able to adjust the screen time on your child's phone.

How to start using Kids360:
install Kids360 on your phone
install Alli360 on your child’s phone and enter the code you see in Kids360
allow monitoring of your child's smartphone in the Kids360 app

You can see your child's screen time on your smartphone for free once your child's device is connected. Time management features in apps (scheduling, blocking apps) are available both in a trial period and with a paid subscription.

The Kids360: parental control app asks for the following permissions:
1. Display over other apps - to block applications when time has run out
2. Special access- to limit screen time
3. Access to usage data - to collect statistics about the apps' running time
4. Autorun - to keep the app tracker running on your child's device at all times
5. Device administrator - to protect against unauthorised deletion and keep kids mode

If you have technical problems, you can always contact Kids360's 24/7 support team by e-mail support@kids360.app
summary: Parental control: child monitoring app, screen time control, GPS child tracker

title: Car Jam Solver: Traffic Jam
description:
🧠 Welcome to Car Jam Solver - Traffic Jam, a brain teaser that will challenge your car sort skills! Ready to tackle a colorful world of car parking games? 🚗👥

🎮 Bus Sort Game Instructions:
Similar to other car parking games, this casual car jam game requires strategic planning and precision to succeed. Observe the line-up of passengers in Car Jam Solver - Traffic Jam, noting the sequence and color matching required in Car Jam Solver - Traffic Jam. Strategically plan and execute your moves to ensure each passenger boards a car in the correct order. Adaptivity and foresight are essential as you work to clear each parking jam from the bus sort game efficiently. 

🌟 Bus Sort Games Features:
- Engaging Car Sort Puzzle Mechanics: Dive into an innovative car sort gameplay where you must match passengers with cars in bus traffic jam based on colors. Strategy is key as difficulty increases progressively, offering seldom-seen brainteasers designed to stretch your cognitive abilities.

- Strategic Prop Utilization: Mastering diverse props simplifies complex challenges and keeps car sort puzzles engaging.

Finish each bus sort and strategically clear parking jam as you step into the car sort challenge and prove your prowess in the engaging puzzle and brainteaser car parking games today!

title: Solitaire
description:
The classical Solitaire you played on computer, now you can play it on your phone!

You will see all the classical elements but with more new features, such as a time reminder which is designed for helping users to manage their time on this game. We know it's fun, but don't get too addicted!

Now, get your brain exercise and dive into the new mobile Solitaire with all the beautiful backgrounds of your choice!

Features:

+ Multiple language choices
+ Can choose whether one or three cards are drawn from the deck at a time
+ Can Choose playing by left hand or right hand
+ Multiple choice backgrounds and cards with different face styles. 
+ Click & Draw function, when you click on one card, it can automatic move to the right place
+ HINT can guide to move next
+ Auto save incomplete game
+ Unlimited UNDO
+ Can be timed for additional points if the game is won.

title: Guitar Band: Rock Battle
description:
Looking for an epic music game to play on your mobile or tablet? Look no further than Guitar Band: Rock Battle – the ultimate rock band challenge! With a mix of bands and rhythm, you can compete against real players from around the world in this free multiplayer game. Featuring amazing guitars that let you test your skills, Guitar Band: Rock Battle takes you on a journey from the garage to the hall of fame.

As you progress through different stages, stadiums, and arenas, you'll have the opportunity to play famous tunes and become a rock n roll hero. With the ability to buy multiple guitars, hire musicians, and make your band famous, you can conquer millions of fans and become a music superstar! Choose from replicas of famous guitars like Fender, Epiphone, Kramer, Gibson, and more – no black or white tiles, just pure, fast, and challenging tap revenge.

Guitar Band: Rock Battle lets you collect and customize super detailed unique guitars, and start your band in the garage, evolving by doing shows, recording albums, and video clips. Assemble your own band by hiring a bassist, drummer, guitarist, and vocalist, just like in a real band. Play in perfect tempo to become a rock and roll hero and conquer success. And the best part? Guitar Band Battle is completely free to play, with in-game purchases available if you want to enhance your gameplay.

So if you're a fan of Kiss, Offspring,The Who, Eric Clapton or any other famous band, Guitar Band Battle is the perfect game for you! Whether you're looking to test your skills against other players from around the world or just enjoy an exciting rhythm game, Guitar Band Battle has something for everyone. Download now and start your journey to becoming a music superstar!

- Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcG7S46CHEir8xoYRMLxVtg

title: Solitaire Story
description: 🚀 Solitaire Game x Rescue Story Episode 💥 All-new Classic Solitaire card game, enriched with thrilling story episodes! 👻 HURRY UP! 😱 The fate of the rescue mission lies in your hands! title: Dancing Road: Sprint & Match
description:
Let's dance down the music road with Dancing Road!

Swipe, sprint, hop, and match colorful balls on the beats - all at once in a rush run! Boost yourself to the next level beats now. It’s easy as abc. Ready to sprint & match balls on the dance road?

🎵 Why Dancing Road is the Ultimate Music Game for You?
- Epic Music Variety: Dive into a sea of songs ranging from the hottest EDM tracks to classic pop hits. The music game revolution is here, and it's waiting for you to take the lead!
- Ball Game Like No Other: Forget about going balls or simple piano tiles. This is a ball game that's all about timing, reflexes, and of course, the beat!
- Rhythm and Rush Combined: It's not just a rhythm game; it's an attractive rush. Keep up with the pace, match the colors, and stay on track!

🌟 Features That Make You Keep Coming Back
- Dance to Your Own Beat: With over 100 songs from various genres, there's always a new challenge waiting. Whether you're into hip hop, rap, or EDM, we've got your playlist sorted.
- Rewards Galore: Who doesn't love rewards? Collect coins and gift boxes to unlock new musical experiences and customization options.
- Challenge Yourself: From easy to hard, there's a range of difficulty levels to keep both beginners and rhythm game veterans engaged.
- Free to Play, Fun to Master: Jump into the fun for free! While there are in-app purchases, the magic of the game is accessible to everyone.

🔥 Dancing Road is Not Just a Game, It's an Experience
- Visually Stunning: With vibrant visuals and dynamic effects, each session is a feast for your eyes.
- Always Fresh: Regular updates mean new songs, features, and challenges. The music never stops!
- Community and Competition: Join a global community of players. Compare scores, share tips, and see who truly has the best rhythm.

💃 Dancing Road is Perfect for You If...
- You love music games, ball games, song games, or just looking for a new way to experience your favorite tunes.
- You crave a game that combines skill, timing, and the joy of music.
- You want a game that's easy to pick up but offers endless hours of entertainment.

🎉 Join the Dancing Road Family Today!
Are you ready to embark on a musical journey like no other? To feel the rush of matching tiles to the beat, to experience the joy of hopping along to your favorite songs? Download Dancing Road now and let the music take control!
Remember, the road is waiting. Your ball, your music, your rhythm. Let's play, let's dance, let's experience the magic of Dancing Road together! 🎶🕺

(Note: Dancing Road is a free-to-play game, but it includes optional in-app purchases for those who want to enhance their experience even further.)

title: Alibaba.com - B2B marketplace
description:
What is Alibaba.com?
Alibaba.com is one of the world’s leading B2B ecommerce marketplaces. Our app allows you to source products from global suppliers, all from the convenience of your mobile device.

Purchase with confidence
Our Trade Assurance service protects your orders and payments on the platform, letting you purchase securely and conveniently with extended support.

Customizable products
Meet suppliers with years of customization and order fulfillment experience for sellers on Amazon, eBay, Wish, Etsy, Mercari, Lazada, Temu and more.

Easy sourcing
Discover millions of ready-to-ship products in every industry category. Tell suppliers what you need and get quotes quickly with Request for Quotation services.

Fast shipping
Alibaba.com partners with major freight forwarders to provide land, sea, and air shipping solutions with on-time delivery services, end-to-end tracking, and competitive prices.

Livestreams and factory tours
Interact with manufacturers in real-time via product demos and tours of manufacturing facilities, providing insight and oversight on how your products are made.

Popular categories and trade shows
Source a wide range of popular items – from trending consumer goods to raw materials – and join our annual trade shows for niche product highlights and discounts.

Quality control
Choose Alibaba.com Production Monitoring and Inspection Services to reduce production delay and quality risks.

Discounts and promotions
Unlock new discounts and promotions from featured manufacturers and suppliers.

Stay updated
Use the Alibaba.com app to stay up to date on new products and promotions from your favorite suppliers.

Language and currency support
Alibaba.com supports 16 languages and 140 local currencies. Use our real-time translator to communicate with sellers in your mother tongue.

title: Aha World: Doll Dress-Up Game
description:
Jump into Aha World, the most amazing role-playing game ever! You can create and dress up dolls, build and design your dream house, simulate daily life in a bustling mini world, and embark on thrilling adventures in tons of fantasy world games.

DRESS UP YOUR DOLL
In this world game, design a variety of doll avatars for your avatar life! Create endless combinations of body shapes, facial features, and hairstyles, then apply stunning makeup. Choose from hundreds of clothes, accessories, and shoes to style your unique life world. Express your personality—pink fashion? Princess style? Or design a brand-new look, just like in your favorite life simulation games!

ROLE PLAYING
Everyone in Aha World is under your control! Choose expressions, voices, and actions for your dolls. You can be a doctor, a police officer, or a pop superstar—your avatar life is what you make it! If life simulation games feel dull, battle dragons or explore the icy Polar Regions in this mini world!

DESIGN YOUR HOME
What is your dream home? A pink princess apartment or a villa with a pool? Use 3000+ furniture items or DIY design unique pieces for your avatar life in these life simulation games. Create life world memories with your dolls!

LIFE SIMULATION
Experience lifestyles in the city: care for babies, shop, or explore city life locations like schools and hospitals. This world game lets you explore a mini world of life simulation games and enjoy your avatar life.

MAGIC AND ADVENTURE
Dive into underwater treasures or frozen realms in this world game. Walk through fairy tale forests or Dino Land with your doll avatar—your avatar life is limitless in these life simulation games!

GAME FEATURES
· Over 500 stylish outfits in various styles
· More than 400 dolls and over 200 kinds of animals and pets, from life world to fantasy mini worlds
· Over 3000 pieces of furniture
· DIY design unique clothing and furniture
· Weather control to experience sun, rain, snow, and day-night changes in these life simulation games.
· Discover hundreds of puzzles and hidden Easter egg secrets across the life world.
· Exciting surprise gifts available regularly
· Offline game, play without Wi-Fi or an internet connection

Aha World—your life world of role-playing game magic! Create, explore, and live your avatar life.

Contact us: contact@ahaworld.com

title: Official Spurs + Stadium App
description:
Your key to Spurs and Tottenham Hotspur Stadium. From exclusive content and features to live concerts & events. Our App gives fans unlimited access to all-things Spurs and Tottenham Hotspur Stadium.
Fan Favourites
·      Digital Tickets: Access your home matchday tickets within the app and enjoy contactless and quick entry into the Stadium.
·      Match Centre: Every minute. Every stat. Every goal. From the first kick of the game to the final whistle, don’t miss any of the action.
·      SPURSPLAY: Our home for exclusive live and on-demand video including the latest highlights, exclusive interviews, classic matches, and insightful documentaries.
·      Membership Hub: Discover exclusive content, behind-the-scenes access, and additional members-only benefits all in one place.
·      Ticket Memories: Reflect on the matches you attended by uploading photos and videos of your favourite moments; from your first Spurs match to seeing an iconic hat trick.
·      Fan Profile: Personalise your very own digital kit, pick your favourite player, and so much more.
Every minute. Every stat. Every goal. From the first kick of the game to the final whistle, don’t miss any of the action thanks to our Match Centre. Premier League or WSL football, home or away, wherever the team or you happen to be in the world, our App makes sure you can follow and listen to the live scores straight from your phone. Matchdays are better than ever.
Let’s keep you in-the-know – as it happens, when it happens. Whether it’s the latest transfer deals to Club announcements and everything in between, only we break Spurs news, everyone else reports it. The Spurs + Stadium App is your go-to for every unmissable moment taking place at Tottenham Hotspur Stadium.
Watch the latest videos on SPURSPLAY, our home for exclusive live and on-demand video including the latest highlights, exclusive interviews, classic matches, and insightful documentaries. Here you can see:
• All Men’s pre-season friendlies live
• Hours of exclusive behind-the-scenes footage
• Live and on-demand Academy matches
• Selected live Women’s matches and all full-match replays on demand
Give great performances the recognition they deserve. Whether it’s a goal-of-the-season contender, a solid display at the back, or a wonder save that caught your attention, have your say on who you think is Player of the Match for every Spurs game by placing your vote in the Official Spurs App.
Tottenham Hotspur Stadium is home to world-class sports and entertainment year-round. See it. Hear it. Live it. Whether it’s for football, live music, events or the NFL, the Official Spurs + Stadium App is your key to Tottenham Hotspur Stadium when you switch to our Stadium mode. Why not make a day of it with our amazing attractions including karting and the DARE Skywalk or discover our premium experiences and award-winning venue that exceeds expectations and lights up the imagination. Our App features all the tools you need to plan your day to Tottenham Hotspur Stadium from an interactive map to travel information.

[Game Goal]:
The main purpose of the game is to remove all cards from the table, assembling them in the tableau before removing them. Initially, 54 cards are dealt to the tableau in ten piles, face down except for the top cards. The tableau piles build down by rank, and in-suit sequences can be moved together. The 50 remaining cards can be dealt to the tableau ten at a time when none of the piles are empty.

title: Muslim Prayer - Qibla Compass
description:
Need a simple Muslim app to find Qibla, prayer times, and Hijri dates in one place?

Stay connected to your Deen with our complete Muslim Qibla app. Accurately find Qibla direction, get prayer times based on your location, and view the Islamic Hijri calendar. Our app brings essential Islamic features with a clean and disciplined design, perfect for every Muslim.

This is your all-in-one Muslim app made to support your everyday Islamic life. Everything is right here, whether you want to find the Qibla direction, check prayer times, or follow the Hijri calendar. But it doesn’t stop there, we’ve also added powerful features like daily Duas and Azkar, beautiful views of Islamic historical places, and even Live streaming from Makkah and Madinah. You can read the Quran Majeed with translations, listen to it with multiple Qaris, and explore Tafseer to understand the deeper meaning of every verse.

🌙 Key Features
🧭 Find the Qibla Direction – Wherever You Are
 Use our built-in compass to quickly find the Qibla. Whether you're at home, school, work, or on a trip, just open the app and know exactly where to face for prayer.
🕌 Accurate Prayer Times for Your Location
 Get daily prayer times for Fajr, Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, and Isha. The app auto-updates the time based on your city.
🔔 Azan Alerts and Prayer Reminders
 Never miss Salah again. Set soft or loud Azan notifications to remind you before or at the time of prayer.
📆 Islamic Hijri Calendar
 Follow the Hijri calendar with ease. Stay informed about important Islamic days like Ramadan, Eid, Hajj, and more with gentle reminders.
📍 Auto Location Detection
The app uses GPS to set your prayer times and Qibla direction. No need to adjust anything, it just works, wherever you go.
📖 Quran Majeed with Translations
 Read the Holy Quran with translations in multiple languages so you can understand every verse in the language that speaks to your heart.
🔊 Listen to Quran by Multiple Qaris
 Enjoy listening to beautiful recitations of the Quran from a wide range of famous Qaris. Choose the one that inspires you the most.
🧠 Quran Tafseer in Different Languages
 Go deeper with Tafseer in many languages. Understand the meaning and context of each Surah and Ayah clearly and simply.
🌟 Check in for 7 Days – Get Rewards
 Stay active in your Imaan journey. Open the app daily for 7 days and unlock a special reward designed to uplift your spiritual goals.
🤲 Daily Duas and Azkar
 Start and end your day with peace. Access a collection of authentic daily Duas and Azkar, great for morning, evening, or anytime your heart needs calm.
📿 Digital Tasbih Counter
 Make Dhikr on the go with a built-in Tasbih counter. It's easy, simple, and always in your pocket.
✨ 99 Names of Allah (Asma-ul-Husna)

title: Baby Panda: Dental Care
description:
Is being a dentist your dream job? Then you must not miss this game! Come to play at Baby Panda's dental salon! Experience the work of a dentist, manage a dental salon to clean and care for little animals' teeth! Become an excellent dentist! 

Content: 
Clean teeth
Little bunny's teeth are so dirty! Food debris is stuck to her teeth: candies, vegetables...help her clean them up! Take out a magnifying glass and find the dirty debris on the teeth. Remove candies and vegetable debris to finish the cleaning! Don't forget to brush teeth thoroughly! 

Remove decayed teeth
Tooth moths are coming for attack! Little hippo's teeth have been attacked! Are you ready? Remove decayed teeth and beat the tooth moths! Observe carefully. Which tooth has cavity? Remove the decayed tooth, clean the cavity, kill the bacteria, and replace with a new tooth! Give it a try and see if you can successfully beat the tooth moths. 

Fix teeth
As a dentist, it's time for you to show your talents! Help the little mouse to fix his teeth. Polish the chipped teeth. Fill in with dentures of the same shape as the chipped teeth. The teeth will be fixed soon! You are awesome! You are indeed an excellent dentist! 

There are other little animals that need your treatment at the dental salon. So what are you waiting for? Hurry up and care for their teeth! 

Features: 
- Experience the work of a little dentist! 
- Care for the teeth of 5 little animals: bunny, monkey, hippo, cat, and mouse!

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 400 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

title: Clash of Clans
description:
Join millions of players worldwide as you build your village, raise a clan, and compete in epic Clan Wars!

Mustachioed Barbarians, fire wielding Wizards, and other unique troops are waiting for you! Enter the world of Clash!

Classic Features:
● Join a Clan of fellow players or start your own and invite friends.
● Fight in Clan Wars as a team against millions of active players across the globe.
● Test your skills in the competitive Clan War Leagues and prove you’re the best.
● Forge alliances, work together with your Clan in Clan Games to earn valuable Magic items.
● Plan your unique battle strategy with countless combinations of Spells, Troops, and Heroes!
● Compete with the best players from around the world and rise to the top of the Leaderboard in Legend League.
● Collect resources and steal loot from other players to upgrade your own Village and turn it into a stronghold. 
● Defend against enemy attacks with a multitude of Towers, Cannons, Bombs, Traps, Mortars, and Walls.
● Unlock epic Heroes like the Barbarian King, Archer Queen, Grand Warden, Royal Champion, and Battle Machine. 
● Research upgrades in your Laboratory to make your Troops, Spells, and Siege Machines even more powerful.
● Create your own custom PVP experiences through Friendly Challenges, Friendly Wars, and special live events.
● Watch Clanmates attack and defend in real-time as a spectator or check out the video replays.
● Fight against the Goblin King in a single player campaign mode through the realm.
● Learn new tactics and experiment with your army and Clan Castle troops in Practice Mode.
● Journey to the Builder Base and discover new buildings and characters in a mysterious world.
● Turn your Builder Base into an unbeatable fortress and defeat rival players in Versus Battles. 
● Collect exclusive Hero Skins and Sceneries to customize your Village.

What are you waiting for, Chief? Join the action today.

PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. The game also includes random rewards.

A network connection is also required.

If you have fun playing Clash of Clans, you may also enjoy other Supercell games like Clash Royale, Brawl Stars, Boom Beach, and Hay Day. Make sure to check those out!

Support: Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/index.html or http://supr.cl/ClashForum or contact us in game by going to Settings > Help and Support.

Privacy Policy: http://www.supercell.net/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service: http://www.supercell.net/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide: http://www.supercell.net/parents

title: Cup Heroes
description:
Cup Heroes: Join the Adventure of a Lifetime! 

Step into the whimsical world of Cup Heroes, where everyday cups turn into mighty heroes on an epic quest to save their beloved Queen! 

This fun-filled adventure will keep you hooked with its charming characters, exciting gameplay, and endless challenges. 

How to Play: 
- Control Your Heroes: Swipe, tap, and drag to navigate your heroes through various obstacles and puzzles. 
- Save the Queen: Your ultimate goal is to rescue the Queen who has been captured by evil forces. 
- Unlock and Upgrade Characters: Collect coins and gems to unlock a diverse cast of characters, each with unique abilities. Upgrade their skills to make them even more powerful and adaptable to different challenges. 

Key Features: 
- Unique Characters: Meet a colourful cast of cup heroes, from the brave Knight Cup to the cunning Ninja Cup. Each character brings their own special skills and personality to the team. 
- Epic Adventures: Explore various enchanting worlds, from mystical forests to fiery volcanoes. Every level is a new adventure filled with hidden secrets and dangerous foes. 
- Challenging Puzzles: Test your brain with mind-bending puzzles that require clever solutions. Use your heroes’ abilities to overcome obstacles and progress through the game. 
- Exciting Battles: Engage in thrilling combat with evil minions and powerful bosses. Use your heroes’ special moves and teamwork to defeat enemies and save the Queen. 
- Beautiful Graphics: Enjoy stunning, colourful graphics that bring the world of Cup Heroes to life. Each scene is meticulously designed to enhance your gaming experience. 
- Daily Rewards and Events: Log in every day for special rewards and participate in limited-time events to earn exclusive items and characters. 

Why You'll Love Cup Heroes: 
- Addictive Gameplay: Easy to learn but hard to master, Cup Heroes offers endless fun for players of all ages. 
- Engaging Storyline: Immerse yourself in a heartwarming story of bravery, teamwork, and the quest to save the Queen. 

Download Cup Heroes now and embark on an unforgettable journey to save the Queen! 
Your cup heroes are waiting for you to lead them to victory!

title: Spotify: Music and Podcasts
description:
With the Spotify music and podcast app, you can play millions of songs, albums and original podcasts for free. We have even added audiobooks, so you can enjoy thousands of stories wherever you are!

Stream music and podcasts, listen to audiobooks, discover albums, playlists or even single songs for free on your mobile or tablet. Subscribe to Spotify Premium to download and listen offline wherever you are.

Spotify gives you access to a world of free music, curated playlists, artists, and podcasts you love. Discover podcasts, new music, top songs or listen to your favorite artists and albums.

WHY SPOTIFY FOR MUSIC AND PODCASTS?
• Listen to over 80 million songs and 4 million podcasts (and counting)
• Enjoy over 300,000 newly added audiobook titles
• Discover new music, albums, playlists and original podcasts.
• Search for your favorite song or artist by typing a lyric
• Enjoy amazing sound quality on music and podcasts across all devices.
• Create and share your own music playlists to suit your mood or discover other playlists you might like.
• Listen to daily music mixes made just for you.
• Explore top songs from different genres, countries or decades.
• Subscribe to your favourite podcasts so that you never miss an episode, then curate your very own podcast library.
• Bookmark individual podcasts into Playlists
• Listen to music and podcasts on your mobile, tablet, desktop, PlayStation, Chromecast, TV, Wear OS or wearable device.

Listen and discover the latest music from artists like;
• Bad Bunny
• Billie Eilish
• Renzo Pianciola
• The Temper Trap
• Harry Styles

Listen to your favorite music artists all day every day via the Popular Radio playlist feature. Here are just some of the artists we’ve already curated;
• Taylor Swift
• Drake
• Eminem
• Coldplay
• Paolo Nutini
• Fleetwood Mac

Listen to over 40 category genres - New Releases, Charts, Live Events, Made for You, At Home, Only You, Summer, Pop, Workout, Hip-Hop, Mood, Party, Pride, Dance/Electronic, Alternative, Indie, Equal, Wellness, Rock, Frequency, R&B, Disney,, Throwback, Radar, Chill, Sleep, In the car, Kids & Family, Caribbean, Classical, Romance, Jazz, Instrumental, Afro, Christian and Gospel and Country.

Listen to popular and exclusive podcasts like;
• The Joe Rogan Experience
• Modern Wisdom
• 2 Bears, 1 Cave with Tom Segura and Bert Kreischer
• Call Her Daddy and Crime Junkie

Search, discover and play music, podcasts and audiobooks from all over the world for free, anywhere, anytime or create your own music playlists with the latest songs to suit your mood.

WHY GO PREMIUM?
• Listen to albums and playlists without ad breaks.
• Download and listen to music and podcasts offline, wherever you are.
• Jump back in and listen to your top songs with on-demand playback.
• Choose from 4 subscription options – Individual, Duo, Family, Student. There’s no commitment and you can cancel any time

Audiobooks in Premium currently available in Australia, the UK & the US. Discover 250,000+ titles, 15 hours/month of available listening for Premium Individual subscribers and Duo & Family plan managers.

Experience Spotify on your Wear OS device:
• Enjoy your favourite music and podcasts without having your phone around.
• Control playback on your phone or any of your Spotify compatible devices.
• Download your favourite content for offline listening on the go (Premium only).
• Get instant access to Spotify with our Tiles and Complications.

Please note: This app features Nielsen’s audience measurement software which will allow you to contribute to market research, such as Nielsen’s Audio Measurement. If you don't want to participate, you can opt-out within the app settings. To learn more about our digital audience measurement products and your choices in regard to them, please visit https://www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.

title: Sporcle Party: Social Trivia
description:
From Sporcle, the world's largest trivia company, comes Sporcle Party. Challenge friends to topics from movies, geography, sports, literature, history and so much more. OR make your own pack. Perfect for office parties, classroom fun, baby showers and playing with friends - in person or virtually.

Get the Party going with your friends in this FREE trivia game from the greatest trivia company on the planet.

KEY FEATURES
• Free, fun and addictive trivia game experience
• Play with your friends and family
• Compete against people from around the world
• Wager points from 1-10 based on how confident you are in your answer
• Create your own packs and share them with anyone
• Thousands of questions and answers across all sorts of topics

You can find hours of trivia entertainment right on your phone, so grab some friends and get started!

title: Erudite: Trivia Games & Quiz
description:
🎲 Games, Puzzles & Brainteasers You’ll Actually Want to Play

If you’re into games that spark your brain, puzzles that make you think, or brainteasers that feel more fun than frustrating — Erudite is your new favorite brain buddy. It’s not just another quiz app. It’s your daily dose of clever, calming question games, playful trivia spin rounds, and unexpected facts that somehow stick. Ideal for your morning coffee, late-night chill, or those five minutes between meetings. Designed to be more than just time-killers, these puzzles and brainteasers are perfect for anyone who wants to keep their brain active without diving into textbook territory. Whether you’re winding down after a long day or trying to beat your best friend in a random quiz challenge, Erudite’s guessing games turn everyday downtime into light, brain-boosting fun.

🧠 Train Your Brain, No Pressure

Erudite’s brain teaser games and quizzes are built for cognitive training — but don’t worry, it never feels like studying. Think of it like mental yoga: the more you play, the sharper you feel. If you’ve ever zoned out with mindless scrolling, this is your chance to swap that habit for something that actually boosts your brainpower. Tap through fun question games that wake up your logic, memory, and problem-solving skills — whether you're at the airport, on your lunch break, or just waiting for the coffee to brew.

☁️ A Chill Way to De-Stress with Question Games

These aren’t the kind of trivia games that leave you frustrated. With no timers or pressure, Erudite offers a mellow space to let go of the day’s chaos. Picture this: you’ve had a long day, you’re curled up on the couch, and instead of binge-scrolling, you open the app for a few lighthearted guessing games that relax your mind but still keep it engaged. This is what self-care for your brain looks like — just you, your thoughts, and a few chill trivia games.

🎓 Learn Without Realizing You’re Learning

Erudite makes learning feel like a casual trivial pursuit — knowledge just slips in. Whether you're curious about how volcanoes work, want to level up your vocabulary, or finally figure out which U.S. state is actually the flattest, our trivia games make learning feel like play. With each trivia spin and clever question games, you're soaking up real facts — no textbooks needed. Perfect for those moments when you want to feel smart, but also kinda lazy.

🎯 Your Daily Trivial Pursuit: New Questions Across Topics

Every day brings fresh quizzes — and you never know what you'll get: 🏛️ History (no more awkward “I should know this” moments) ➕ Math (surprise yourself with how fast you can calculate a tip) 🌍 Geography (so next time you travel, you’re not totally lost) 🔬 Science (because weird facts about space are always cool) 💬 Linguistics (fancy words = bonus points in Scrabble) 🎵 Music (spot melodies your friends completely miss)

🏆 No Pressure, Just Progress

Each question gives you three tries — so if you mess up, no sweat. Erudite rewards curiosity, not perfection. You’ll rack up points with fun guessing games and quizzes, while every small win keeps your brain feeling fresh. It’s like a low-stakes trivial pursuit, where you’re competing against yesterday’s version of you.

💬 Quizzes & Clever Facts That Stick With You

You know those random facts you drop into conversations that make everyone stop and go, “Wait, really?” Yeah, that’s Erudite working its trivial pursuit magic. One minute you’re diving into trivia games and guessing games while your pasta’s boiling, the next you’re impressing your friends with some offbeat facts from a quick trivia spin. So if you're looking for guessing games or trivia games that relax your brain, question games that sharpen your wit, or quizzes that teach without preaching — it’s time to play smarter with Erudite. You might just become the walking trivial pursuit champion of your group.

title: Crossword Master - Word Puzzle
description:
Crossword Master is a turn-based word game where you and your opponent work together to complete a crossword puzzle while competing for the highest score. Dive into this highly addictive experience and enjoy endless fun! Solve crosswords, outsmart your opponents, and become a word master!

Crossword Master combines the best elements of word puzzle games and classic crosswords with modern and intuitive gameplay, making it suitable for both expert wordsmiths and casual players. Inspired by Scandinavian-style crosswords, Crossword Master features clues within the cells to enhance gameplay convenience.

Discover a fresh take on daily crossword puzzles: draw letters from the deck, and craft words according to the clues. Some of the clues are pictures, which adds an extra layer of challenge and fun! If you enjoy word games for adults, daily newspaper crosswords, anagrams and logic puzzles, try this captivating crossword puzzle game, and you won't be able to put it down!

Are you ready to challenge your vocabulary and sharpen your mind with an exciting word game? Crossword Master strikes the perfect balance between entertainment and a useful brain exercise. Each crossword puzzle is carefully designed to train your language skills, spelling, logic, and general knowledge. Explore thousands of words, enrich your vocabulary, and master the art of crossword games!

What you get:

✔ Engaging crossword game with smooth graphics and a modern look
✔ Plenty of unique free crossword puzzles for adults packed with countless words to unravel, keeping you hooked for hours!
✔ Enhancing your vocabulary. Learn new words and their meanings while playing crossword games for free
✔ Hints available to assist when you're stuck solving crossword puzzles and need a clue
✔ Auto-save ensures you can resume any unfinished crossword anytime without losing your progress
✔ No time limit. Enjoy this free crossword game at your own pace
✔ New crossword puzzle game from a top developer, guaranteeing quality and fun.

How to play Crossword Master:

- Your goal in this turn-based word game is to craft words on the crossword board according to the clues and outscore your opponent.
- Use blue cells with clues to guess words in this engaging crossword puzzle game. Find the right fit for each letter from a set of five and place them one by one from the deck to start forming words.
- Try to place all the letters from the deck in each turn to maximize your score and solve crossword puzzles. Every correct letter earns one point, with additional points awarded for completing words. The score for a whole word equals the number of letters it contains. Aim to construct longer words and multiple words in a single move for the highest scores.
- If you’re stuck playing word puzzle games, tap the Hint button to see possible placements for the letters.
- Confirm your choices by clicking the Submit button once you’ve placed all your letters. The opponents are virtual so you don't waste precious time waiting for your opponent's next move.
- Think strategically while solving crosswords. Sometimes, holding back a crucial letter for a future move can help create a longer word and boost your score potential.
- The crossword game concludes when all words on the board are completed. The player with the highest score at the end is the winner.

Ready to embrace the challenge? Solve daily crossword puzzles anywhere, anytime, stretch your cognitive limits, and become a master of words!

Terms of Use:
https://easybrain.com/terms

Privacy Policy:
https://easybrain.com/privacy

Are you ready to challenge your vocabulary and sharpen your mind with an exciting word game? Crossword Master strikes the perfect balance between entertainment and a useful brain exercise. Each crossword puzzle is carefully designed to train your language skills, spelling, logic, and general knowledge. Explore thousands of words, enrich your vocabulary, and master the art of crossword games!

What you get:

✔ Engaging crossword game with smooth graphics and a modern look
✔ Plenty of unique free crossword puzzles for adults packed with countless words to unravel, keeping you hooked for hours!
✔ Enhancing your vocabulary. Learn new words and their meanings while playing crossword games for free
✔ Hints available to assist when you're stuck solving crossword puzzles and need a clue
✔ Auto-save ensures you can resume any unfinished crossword anytime without losing your progress
✔ No time limit. Enjoy this free crossword game at your own pace
✔ New crossword puzzle game from a top developer, guaranteeing quality and fun.

How to play Crossword Master:

- Your goal in this turn-based word game is to craft words on the crossword board according to the clues and outscore your opponent.
- Use blue cells with clues to guess words in this engaging crossword puzzle game. Find the right fit for each letter from a set of five and place them one by one from the deck to start forming words.
- Try to place all the letters from the deck in each turn to maximize your score and solve crossword puzzles. Every correct letter earns one point, with additional points awarded for completing words. The score for a whole word equals the number of letters it contains. Aim to construct longer words and multiple words in a single move for the highest scores.
- If you’re stuck playing word puzzle games, tap the Hint button to see possible placements for the letters.
- Confirm your choices by clicking the Submit button once you’ve placed all your letters. The opponents are virtual so you don't waste precious time waiting for your opponent's next move.
- Think strategically while solving crosswords. Sometimes, holding back a crucial letter for a future move can help create a longer word and boost your score potential.
- The crossword game concludes when all words on the board are completed. The player with the highest score at the end is the winner.

Ready to embrace the challenge? Solve daily crossword puzzles anywhere, anytime, stretch your cognitive limits, and become a master of words!

Terms of Use:
https://easybrain.com/terms

Privacy Policy:
https://easybrain.com/privacy
summary: Daily crossword puzzles for brain training! Master vocabulary with word games!

title: EA SPORTS FC™ Mobile Soccer
description:
Experience the new Rivals Update with enhanced PVP gameplay & earn even greater rewards as we prepare for the 2025/2026 season of european football. 
 
Play as any team from the Premier League or LALIGA EA SPORTS including Liverpool, Chelsea & Real Madrid in Club Challenge PVP mode or compete for the European Cup in the UEFA Champions League Tournament. Collect Player Items to build your dream Ultimate Team™ with soccer stars Jude Bellingham, Cole Palmer, Phil Foden, Virgil van Dijk, Trent Alexander-Arnold or legendary ICONs like David Beckham & Ronaldinho. FC Mobile has the biggest competitions, leagues, & players across the world with more than 18K fully licensed players, 690+ teams, & 30+ euopean football leagues including the UEFA Champions League.
 
KEY FEATURES
Score goals with the world’s best players as you level up a team of soccer superstars
Join a League & team up to compete in tournaments and collect more rewards
Compete in upgraded PvP football game modes including Club Challenge, 1v1 H2H, VS Attack & Manager Mode
Earn rewards faster with Daily Training, Quests and Achievements
Play as your favourite UCL team & compete to win the European Cup in the official UEFA Champions League Tournament Mode
Watch FCM TV to see game guides, FCM LIVE streams & soccer match content from some of the world’s biggest leagues including LALIGA & MLS

COMPETE HEAD TO HEAD
Play PVP matches to rank up in Division Rivals 
Earn rewards as you climb weekly Leaderboards
Improved ranking system & enhanced matchmaking
Show off with more vanity & customization options

JOIN LEAGUES
Bigger, Better Leagues! Join leagues with up to 100 members
Find friends faster with Leagues tagged by language, clubs, region & more
Team up with your league to play tournaments & earn seasonal rewards

AUTHENTIC GAMEPLAY IMPROVEMENTS
Enhanced Passing System: Move the ball with improved precision & control assistance
Improved Corner Defending: Defenders with better height and jumping stats are now prioritized
Skill Move Balancing: Players’ skill moves scale with player attributes, for greater player authenticity 

CLUB CHALLENGES 
Compete as any authentic English Premier League or LALIGA EA SPORTS Club in a real time multiplayer PVP game
Play as Liverpool, Chelsea, Manchester City or Real Madrid, Atlético de Madrid & many more

FOOTBALL LEAGUES, LEGENDS & COMPETITIONS
Premier League, LALIGA EA SPORTS, UEFA Champions League, Bundesliga, Ligue 1 McDonald’s, Serie A Enilive & many more are playable throughout the season
Play with football legends: Zinedine Zidane, Ronaldinho, David Beckham, Wayne Rooney, Gareth Bale, & more

Join the next generation of soccer / football legends with EA SPORTS FC and play anywhere for the club.
This app: Requires acceptance of EA’s User Agreement and Privacy & Cookie Policy. Do Not Sell My Personal Information: https://tos.ea.com/legalapp/WEBPRIVACYCA/US/en/PC/ Requires an Internet connection (network fees may apply). Allows players (above the minimum age of digital consent in their country) to communicate via League chat; to disable for users under the age of majority with League chat access, use your device's parental controls. Includes in-game advertising. Contains direct links to the Internet and social networking sites intended for an audience over 13. The app uses Google Play Game Services. Log out of Google Play Game Services before installation if you don’t want to share your game play with friends. This game includes optional in-game purchases of virtual currency that can be used to acquire virtual in-game items, including a random selection of virtual in-game items. FC Points not available in Belgium.

User Agreement: terms.ea.com
Privacy and Cookie Policy: privacy.ea.com
Visit help.ea.com for assistance or inquiries.
EA may retire online features after 30 days’ notice posted on ea.com/service-updates.

title: CookieRun: Kingdom
description:
◼︎ EVERYONE'S FAVORITE TINY HEROES: THE COOKIES
Meet our Cookies, all voiced by an amazing cast of voice actors
Witness their epic skills, fall in love with their voices, and dress them into new chic costumes.
Join the Cookies in CookieRun: Kingdom!

◼︎ EMBARK ON AN EPIC JOURNEY AROUND EARTHBREAD
The secrets of the ancient Cookies and their kingdoms are waiting to be unraveled.
Join GingerBrave and his friends against Dark Enchantress Cookie and her dark legion.
The chronicles of CookieRun: Kingdom have just begun!

◼︎ BUILD A DELICIOUSLY SWEET KINGDOM
Choose from a great variety of unique decors to design the Kingdom of your dreams.
Produce materials, craft items, arrange all sorts of activities—the vibrant kingdom life awaits!

◼︎ BATTLE YOUR WAY TO VICTORY
Create the ultimate Cookie team with endless combinations of Treasures and Toppings
Prove your battle skill in the Kingdom Arena, Cookie Alliance, Super Mayhem, and Guild Battles!
Come up with different strategies to emerge victorious!

■ BRING GLORY TO YOUR GUILD
Reach the top of the ranking table with your fellow guildmates.
Expand your guild's Domain and collect Guild Relics to become the strongest guild there is!

[Required Access]
For Android 10 devices or older: 
Storage: allows the app to install the game and save game data
 • READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
 • WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE

For Android 11 devices or newer:
※ If you play the game as a guest, your game data will be deleted upon deleting the app.

[Denying Access]
Select Allow or Deny in Settings, Privacy, or the selected permission

title: DAZN - Watch Live Sports
description:
The Ultimate Sports Entertainment Platform

DAZN is the only truly global pure-play sports entertainment platform. We uniquely integrate the entire fan experience for fans to watch, play, and socialize, all in one place.

Watch Anytime, Anywhere.
Experience sports like never before. Stream your favorite events live or on demand, on any device, from anywhere in the world. DAZN delivers the game to you, wherever you are.

The Home of the FIFA Club World Cup
Strap yourself in. The FIFA Club World Cup is here—a brand-new tournament bringing together 32 of the world’s top football clubs to crown the world's greatest club. Champions will be crowned. Worldwide bragging rights claimed. And just like the Club World Cup, challengers will have to wait four years for another shot at glory. Join us for all the action between 14 June and 13 July.

Play in FanZone and Beyond
Dive into the action with FanZone. Chat live, send reactions, and connect with fellow fans in real-time. It’s your front-row seat to the heart of the game.
Connect with Fans

Join the community. Chat with fans, share your passion, and celebrate every victory together. On DAZN, every game is a social event.

DAZN brings you the ultimate sports streaming experience with a world of content available anytime, anywhere:
• Dive into the “Home of Boxing”, featuring top events, schedules, fighter profiles, and exclusive content, including BKFC (Bare Knuckle Fighting Championship).
• Stay up-to-date with the “Schedule” feature, setting alerts for your favorite games and matches.
• Navigate effortlessly with the new sub-navigation bar to quickly access your favorite competitions like Women’s Football, including Liga F, and Frauen-Bundesliga.
• Get real-time “Stats and Scores” for all games, even those not streaming on DAZN.
• Explore full “Fight Cards” for boxing events and revisit past rounds with a single click.
• Use the enhanced search page to find what you’re looking for swiftly.
• Engage with fans in the “FanZone” by cheering, chatting, sending reactions, and participating in polls.
• Manage your account with ease using the updated profile section.
• Browse and watch a variety of live channels with the EPG for live channels feature, including content like Rally TV, PDC Darts, and more.

DAZN holds the world’s largest portfolio of sports broadcasting rights, including:
• History-making fights from Matchroom Promotions, Queensbury, Golden Boy Promotions, and BKFC.
• NFL Game Pass, with access to every game, and basketball content like Courtside 1891 and action from the NBL.
• The best of live Women’s Football, including Liga F, NWSL, and Frauen-Bundesliga.
• All the action from Professional Fighters League (PFL), MMA events from Naciones MMA, Ansgar Fighting League, and more.
• Enjoy thrilling sports like Tennis, PDC Darts, and global events from Riyadh Season.
• Over 10 linear TV channels on our platform with 24/7 content, including Red Bull TV, Matchroom Snooker, Lacrosse TV, and Padel TIME TV.
• If you love video-on-demand (VOD), explore our extensive library of sports documentaries, features, and shows.

Watch every match of the Club World Cup, exclusively on DAZN, as 32 of the world’s top football clubs compete for global glory
DAZN is your gateway to sports, bringing you closer to the action than ever before.

Terms of Use https://www.dazn.com/en-US/help/articles/pp-tcs-all
Privacy Policy: https://www.dazn.com/en-US/help/articles/pp-tcs-all

title: Umamusume: Pretty Derby
description:
Umamusume: Pretty Derby is ready to race! Scout featured trainees and supporters as you navigate the immersive sports life simulation through the game's in-depth training system and top-of-the-line 3D graphics!

Introduction
-- Umamusume. They are born to run. They inherit otherworldly names, and are inspirited by dreams most dramatic and wonderful. Now, they run ever forward. That, is their destiny. No one knows how the races that lie in their futures will end. Even so, they continue to run, aiming only toward the goal in front of them.

-- Each and every one of the runners sports a unique charm. It's up to you, the trainer, to lead them down the path of victory! You have but one goal—raise your Umamusume to her fullest potential and help turn her greatest dreams into reality. In order to reach these newfound heights, it's your job to participate in—and win—as many races as possible! Triumph awaits those who train hard and work to communicate. Only by cooperating will you take the crown!

-- Experience the thrilling stories of historic racers, such as:

Special Week (Voice: Azumi Waki)
Silence Suzuka (Voice: Marika Kono)
Tokai Teio (Voice: Machico)
Oguri Cap (Voice: Tomoyo Takayanagi)
Gold Ship (Voice: Hitomi Ueda)
Vodka (Voice: Ayaka Ohashi)
Daiwa Scarlet (Voice: Chisa Kimura)
Mejiro McQueen (Voice: Saori Onishi)
Symboli Rudolf (Voice: Azusa Tadokoro)
Rice Shower (Voice: Manaka Iwami)
Haru Urara (Voice: Yukina Shuto)
Nice Nature (Voice: Kaori Maeda)

...and so many more—over 20 Umamusume are searching for a trainer to help them achieve their goals!

-- Cheer for your favorite Umamusume and immerse yourself in exhilarating races and stunning performances in breathtaking 3D graphics. Up to 18 Umamusume compete in races against each other for first place—watch them go as you tune in to the game's incredibly realistic live commentary. And of course, stick around after the race to support the victor during a dazzling winning concert! Whether on the racetrack or the stage, raise the roof to each exciting new performance!

-- Follow us on X:
https://x.com/umamusume_eng

-- For more information, check out our official website:
https://umamusume.com/

title: Baby Panda's Supermarket
description:
In Baby Panda’s Supermarket, you can not only enjoy shopping but also play as a cashier and check out items! Apart from that, there are also many fun events for you to join in the supermarket. Shop in the Supermarket Game with your shopping list now!

A WIDE VARIETY OF GOODS 
The supermarket has a wide variety of goods, including over 300 kinds of goods such as food, toys, children's clothing, fruits, cosmetics, and everyday items. You can buy almost anything you want here! Look carefully, on which shelf are the items you want to buy?

BUY WHAT YOU NEED
Go to the supermarket and shop for Daddy Panda's birthday party! Birthday cake, ice cream, some flowers, birthday presents, and more! Next, let's buy some new school supplies for the upcoming school season! Remember to check your shopping list to make sure you've bought everything you need!

SUPERMARKET EVENTS
If you like to cook delicious food and make crafts, then don't miss out on the supermarket's DIY activities! You can cook any popular gourmet food and make any items you like, such as strawberry cakes, chicken burgers, and festival masks. The supermarket also offers claw machines, capsule toy machines, and other facilities for you to try!

SHOPPING RULES
While shopping in the supermarket, you may also encounter bad behavior such as climbing shelves, running around with carts and jumping the queue. Through the vivid scene interpretation and correct guidance, you will learn the shopping rules in the supermarket, stay out of danger, and shop in a civilized way!

CASHIER EXPERIENCE
Want to use a cash register and try scanning and checking out items? In the supermarket game, you can become a cashier, learn the checkout process, and get to know payment methods like cash and credit cards! Learn numbers and improve your math skills while making the shopping experience more fun!

New stories happen in Baby Panda's Supermarket Game every day. Come and have a great shopping time!

FEATURES:
- A two-storied supermarket: a supermarket game especially designed for kids;
- Restores the real scene: 40+ counters and 300+ kinds of goods;
- Enjoy shopping: food, toys, clothes, fruits, electrical appliances, and more;
- Fun interactions: organizing shelves, grabbing toys from the claw machine, applying makeup, dress-up, food DIY and more;
- Nearly 10 families like the Quacky family and the MeowMi family are looking forward to shopping with you;
- Featured holiday decorations to create a lively atmosphere in the supermarket；
- While shopping in the supermarket, you'll learn the rules of safe shopping;
- Trial services: playing with toys, trying a sample, etc.; 
- Cashier service: Become a cashier and manage cash or credit card payments!

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 600 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations, over 9000 stories  of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

- Nearly 10 families like the Quacky family and the MeowMi family are looking forward to shopping with you;
- Featured holiday decorations to create a lively atmosphere in the supermarket；
- While shopping in the supermarket, you'll learn the rules of safe shopping;
- Trial services: playing with toys, trying a sample, etc.;
- Cashier service: Become a cashier and manage cash or credit card payments!

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 600 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations, over 9000 stories of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

title: Dream Home Coloring book
description:
Welcome to Dream Home Color – Your Ultimate Coloring Adventure!

Unleash your creativity and dive into a world of vibrant hues with our latest game, "Dream Home Color." Immerse yourself in the therapeutic joy of coloring as you transform ordinary houses into stunning masterpieces. Whether you're a seasoned artist or just looking for a relaxing way to unwind, Dream Home Color is the perfect digital canvas for everyone.

Key Features:
1. Endless Coloring Possibilities: Explore a vast array of beautifully illustrated houses waiting for your artistic touch. From cozy cottages to modern mansions, each level offers a unique and enchanting coloring experience.

2. Intuitive Gameplay: Our user-friendly interface ensures a seamless coloring experience for players of all ages. Simply tap to select colors and fill each section with the swipe of a finger. No stress, just pure coloring enjoyment!

3. Rich Color Palette: Choose from a wide spectrum of colors to bring your imagination to life. Experiment with shades, gradients, and patterns to make your creations truly one-of-a-kind. The possibilities are as limitless as your creativity!

4. Soothing Music and Sounds: Immerse yourself in a relaxing atmosphere with our carefully selected background music and soothing sound effects. Let the calming tunes enhance your coloring experience and transport you to a world of tranquility.

5. Save and Share Your Masterpieces: Capture your completed artworks with our easy-to-use save feature. Share your colorful creations with friends and family on social media or use them as wallpapers to brighten up your devices.

6. Daily Challenges: Test your skills with daily coloring challenges. Complete them to earn rewards and unlock special features. Stay engaged and motivated as you embark on a daily coloring journey!

7. No Time Limits or Pressure: Unlike traditional coloring books, Dream Home Color offers a stress-free environment with no time constraints. Take your time, enjoy the process, and let your creativity flow at your own pace.

How to Play:
- Select a house from the diverse range of illustrations.
- Tap to choose your desired color from the palette.
- Swipe your finger across the areas you want to fill with color.
- Experiment with different colors and techniques to perfect your masterpiece.

Why Dream Home Color?
- Relaxing and Therapeutic: Immerse yourself in a calming coloring experience that provides stress relief and relaxation.
- Offline Play: No internet? No problem! Enjoy Dream Home Color anytime, anywhere, without the need for an internet connection.
- Frequent Updates: Stay tuned for new houses, features, and challenges in regular updates. The coloring fun never ends!

Embark on a colorful journey with "Dream Home Color" and turn your creativity into beautiful works of art. Download now and let the coloring adventure begin!

Thank you for choosing Dream Home Color – where imagination meets color!

title: Through the Word
description:
UNDERSTAND THE BIBLE IN JUST TEN MINUTES A DAY, with plans for every book and audio guides for every chapter.

Through the Word is a guided audio journey through the entire Bible, one chapter at a time - with no ads, no fees, ever. Every day, more than 150,000 people around the world trust TTW for their daily Bible habit. Read their stories below!

YOUR DAILY BIBLE HABIT

Simple. Bible. Habit. One chapter today, next chapter tomorrow.

BIBLE ON YOUR SCREEN, TEACHER IN YOUR HEADPHONES

Every audio guide walks you through one Bible chapter with clear explanation and insightful application.

UNDERSTAND THE BIBLE TOGETHER

New in 4.0! TTW Together is now available for every Bible book, journey, and topical plan. Start or join a group today!

FREE FOREVER & 10 MINUTES A DAY

No fees and no ads. TTW fits a busy schedule, making it easy to listen on the road, while you work out, or whatever fits your daily routine… anytime, anywhere, even offline.

AUDIO GUIDES FOR EVERY CHAPTER

From Genesis to Revelation, walk through all 1,189 chapters in about 10 minutes each with clear explanations for every chapter.

19 EPIC JOURNEYS THROUGH THE BIBLE

The Bible can seem daunting, so TTW has broken it down into 19 journeys, guiding you step-by-step through books, themes, and chronology with a great balance between Old and New Testaments.

THE CURE FOR LOST-IN-LEVITICUS SYNDROME

Have you ever started a Bible reading plan, but got bogged down in Leviticus or Numbers? TTW’s simple plan keeps you moving, and our teachers even make the boring chapters interesting!

GUIDES FOR BIBLE CURIOUS TO BIBLE PROS

New to the Bible? Try the 26-day “Start” journey. Been reading for a while now? TTW has more than 1,200 audio guides covering every Bible chapter, with insight and application for every level.

THOUSANDS OF 5-STAR REVIEWS AND LISTENER STORIES

“… Today (Oct 20, 2023) we officially completed 1,288 days straight going through each chapter of each book of the Bible… we have truly become a band of brothers. We’ve seen miraculous answers to prayer… we have become a band of brothers who rally daily around God's Word… You have been an anchor for us." –JD Hornbacher (and the "Bible with the Guys" group) (Oct 20, 2023)

“… TTW has changed my life completely. It made the Bible come alive… Now that I listen before sleeping, I have no trouble keeping the Bible habit… ending the day with my head and thoughts resting and thinking about through the word.” –Christina Thorkildsen (October 9, 2023)

“We do our homeschool Bible class with TTW… Always excellent! Always a blessing. We are die-hard TTW fans… And we love you all!” –Kate Russo Thompson (October 3, 2023)

“I have been a Christian for many years… I learn something new every day. It’s awesome! So thankful Kris and company obeyed the Lord in this incredible undertaking.” –paigebontrager (September 15, 2023)

“… never have I experienced the Bible in this kind of way! Since I downloaded and signed into the app… It feels really great to be excited about God's Word!” –Misty H (September 8, 2023)

Find even more stories at https://throughtheword.org/stories/

title: Skyline Bowling
description:
Welcome to the next level of immersive and exciting gameplay with Skyline Bowling! 🎳 Enter a vibrant and dynamic world where skill, precision, and strategy are your greatest allies. Prepare to embark on a thrilling journey as you strive to dominate the lanes and become the ultimate bowling champion!

Skyline Bowling takes the traditional game of bowling to new heights, offering a multiplayer experience that will keep you captivated for hours on end. Join millions of players from around the globe in real-time matches where every roll counts. Are you ready to claim your place at the top of the leaderboard? 🌐🏅

🏙️ Unique Maps: Bowl through stunning cityscapes and unique maps with dynamic terrain. Strategize your shots to navigate obstacles and outsmart your opponents. Every game is a new adventure!

🎳 Real-Time Multiplayer: Compete against players worldwide in intense multiplayer matches. Show off your skills and rise through the ranks to become the ultimate ruler of Skyline Bowling. Can you emerge victorious?

💪 Power-Up Arsenal: Gain the upper hand with a variety of powerful abilities and enhancements. From speed boosts to precision targeting, choose your power-ups wisely to gain a strategic advantage.

🎨 Customization: Express yourself with a range of skins, themes, and avatars. Whether you're a fierce competitor or a playful bowler, there's a look for every style. Show off your personality and stand out from the crowd!

🏆 Achievements and Rewards: Unlock achievements and earn rewards as you progress through the game. From exclusive skins to in-game currency, there are plenty of incentives to keep you coming back for more.

🎮 Easy to Learn, Hard to Master: With simple controls and addictive gameplay, Skyline Bowling is easy to pick up for players of all skill levels. However, mastering the art of bowling will require strategy and skill.

🎉 Endless Entertainment: With dynamic gameplay and endless possibilities, there's never a dull moment in Skyline Bowling. From epic strikes to hilarious mishaps, you'll be entertained every step of the way!

👑 Become the Legend: Rise from a mere contender to a legendary champion as you conquer more lanes and outsmart your opponents. Leave your mark on the virtual world of Skyline Bowling and etch your name into the annals of history.

Join the millions of players already hooked on Skyline Bowling and experience the thrill of the game like never before. Whether you're a casual gamer looking for some quick fun or a competitive strategist seeking a challenge, Skyline Bowling offers something for everyone. Download now and embark on your quest for bowling domination! 🎳🏆

title: Merge Fellas
description:
Merge Fellas is the ultimate merge puzzle game!

Merge memes in this puzzle game! Challenge your brain and pass the casual time by dropping and merging cute pets. Train your brain by solving the relaxing and cozy puzzle. 
Merge Fellas offers fun and addictive gameplay. Merge Fellas is completely free, no WiFi or internet needed, giving you awesome gaming experience offline and online.

Combine memes to make them bigger!
Be the first to create the Final Boss!
Famous Italian memes are also waiting to be discovered.
The puzzle game features lots of fun and addictive modes: Fellas Mode, Cat Mode, Italian Mode, Meme Mode, Friends Mode, Capybara Mode and more, offering a cozy and satisfying gaming experience.
• Fellas Mode: Aim and drop pets to create new ones. Famous pets await to de discovered. You goal is to create a giant capybara.
• Italian Mode: Here you merge the Italian memes.
• Capybara Mode: Your mission is to merge adorable capybaras and create the cutest, most unique capybaras. Discover unique combinations like the bee capybara, the donut capybara, the cool capybara, capybara with turtle, capybara and the pelican, capybara and the crocodile.

In this free and popular match and merge puzzle game, you don't need WiFi or an internet connection. Even in offline mode, you can use logic and strategy to solve puzzles and enhance your mind. Join this relaxing puzzle journey!

How to play the free Merge Fellas puzzle game:
- Aim and drop pets and memes for sorting and matching.
- Classic merge puzzles require strategic matching of similar memes to create new ones.
- When there is no more space the meme box, the puzzle game will end.
- Use logic and thinking to ensure that the placed pets are the best match, testing your IQ and brain.

Merge Fellas features:
- Completely free, no WiFi needed. Play online or offline and enjoy the fun of drop and merge puzzle games anytime, anywhere.
- Easy and addictive gameplay.
- Suitable for all friends and family.
- Endless merging fun
- Optimization for all screens

Solve the puzzle and merge all the pets and memes! The Final Boss is the ultimate goal. The merge puzzle game can be played offline without WiFi and offers lots of satisfying gameplay experience. Download Merge Fellas for free today and become the best!
